350283,91,900,14,35,1,133,15,"Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi … pe… maraṇassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā."
