350285,91,901,19,48,1,78,9,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu divase nikkhante rattiyā patihitāya[ paṭihitāya( pī.),( a. ni.6.20 passitabbaṃ)] iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
