350319,91,910,15,53,1,154,16,"Katamā aṭṭha?[ a. ni.8.54] Uṭṭhānasampadā, ārakkhasampadā, kalyāṇamittatā, samajīvitā, saddhāsampadā, sīlasampadā, cāgasampadā, paññāsampadā– imā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha sampadā’’ ti."
350320,91,911,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Uṭṭhātā kammadheyyesu, appamatto vidhānavā; "
350321,91,912,2,8,1,43,5,"Samaṃ kappeti jīvikaṃ, sambhataṃ anurakkhati."
