350387,91,938,25,34,1,81,8,"Idhāvuso, bhikkhuno pavivittassa viharato nirāyattavuttino icchā uppajjati lābhāya. "
350388,91,938,35,42,1,37,5,"So uṭṭhahati, ghaṭati, vāyamati lābhāya. "
350389,91,938,43,52,1,57,7,"Tassa uṭṭhahato, ghaṭato, vāyamato lābhāya lābho nuppajjati. "
350390,91,938,53,65,1,79,10,"So tena alābhena socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
