350692,91,1001,2,22,1,135,15,86. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena icchānaṅgalaṃ nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari. 
350693,91,1001,23,29,1,63,6,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe. 
350694,91,1001,30,34,1,45,4,Assosuṃ kho icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
350695,91,1001,35,50,1,122,12,‘‘ samaṇo khalu bho gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito icchānaṅgalaṃ anuppatto icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe . 
350696,91,1001,51,60,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
350697,91,1001,61,82,1,95,14,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho… pe… sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’’ ti. 
350698,91,1002,2,16,1,145,14,Atha kho icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tassā rattiyā accayena pahutaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ ādāya yena icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
350699,91,1002,17,22,1,60,5,upasaṅkamitvā bahidvārakoṭṭhake aṭṭhaṃsu uccāsaddā mahāsaddā. 
350700,91,1002,23,32,1,61,9,Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nāgito bhagavato upaṭṭhāko hoti. 
350701,91,1002,33,39,1,44,6,Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ nāgitaṃ āmantesi–
350702,91,1002,40,56,1,67,10,"‘‘ ke pana te, nāgita, uccāsaddā mahāsaddā kevaṭṭā maññe macchavilope’’ ti?"
350703,91,1002,57,77,1,148,14,"‘‘ Ete, bhante, icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā pahutaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ ādāya bahidvārakoṭṭhake ṭhitā bhagavantaṃyeva uddissa bhikkhusaṅghañcā’’ ti."
350704,91,1002,78,91,1,45,8,"‘‘ Māhaṃ, nāgita, yasena samāgamaṃ, mā ca mayā yaso. "
350705,91,1002,92,106,1,134,12,"Yo kho, nāgita, nayimassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī assa akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. "
350706,91,1002,107,148,1,184,15,"Yassāhaṃ nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī[ nikāmalābhī assaṃ( bahūsu) a. ni.5.30 passitabbaṃ. tattha hi ayaṃ pāṭhabhedā natthi] akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, so taṃ mīḷhasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ lābhasakkārasilokasukhaṃ sādiyeyyā’’ ti."
