350710,91,1003,21,36,1,107,13,"Yena yeneva dāni, bhante, bhagavā gamissati tanninnāva bhavissanti brāhmaṇagahapatikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca. "
350711,91,1003,37,48,1,78,8,"Seyyathāpi , bhante, thullaphusitake deve vassante yathāninnaṃ udakāni pavattanti; "
