351012,92,55,21,43,1,137,17,"Yathā yathā, āvuso, bhikkhu bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ… pe… brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti, tathā tathā naṃ sabrahmacārī uttari sambhāventi–"
351013,92,55,44,52,1,36,6,‘ addhā ayamāyasmā patto vā pajjati vā’. 
