351127,92,76,2,13,1,57,7,7. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. 
351128,92,76,14,21,1,54,7,Atha kho sutavā paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
351129,92,76,22,26,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
