351190,92,93,178,190,1,60,8,‘‘ Evamāvuso’’ ti kho āyasmā sāriputto tassa bhikkhuno paccassosi. 
351191,92,94,2,50,1,98,14,"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ca mahāmoggallāno[ mahāmoggalāno( ka.)] āyasmā ca ānando avāpuraṇaṃ[ apāpuraṇaṃ( syā. ka.)] ādāya vihāre āhiṇḍanti[ vihārena vihāraṃ anvāhiṇḍanti( sī. pī.), vihāraṃ āhiṇḍanti( syā.)]–"
351192,92,94,51,56,1,41,2,"‘‘ abhikkamathāyasmanto, abhikkamathāyasmanto! "
