351227,92,105,2,16,1,116,14,Atha kho so bhikkhu uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
351228,92,105,17,38,1,133,16,"‘‘ accayo maṃ, bhante, accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, yo ahaṃ āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ asatā tucchā musā abhūtena abbhācikkhiṃ. "
351229,92,105,39,53,1,73,10,"Tassa me, bhante, bhagavā accayaṃ accayato paṭiggaṇhatu āyatiṃ saṃvarāyā’’ ti."
351230,92,105,54,84,1,129,16,"‘‘ Taggha taṃ[ tvaṃ( sī. pī.)], bhikkhu, accayo accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, yo tvaṃ sāriputtaṃ asatā tucchā musā abhūtena abbhācikkhi. "
351231,92,105,85,103,1,97,14,"Yato ca kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ paṭikarosi, taṃ te mayaṃ paṭiggaṇhāma. "
351232,92,105,104,122,1,112,14,"Vuḍḍhihesā, bhikkhu, ariyassa vinaye yo accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ paṭikaroti āyatiṃ saṃvaraṃ āpajjatī’’ ti. "
351233,92,106,2,9,1,47,6,Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi–
351234,92,106,10,52,1,84,11,"‘‘ khama, sāriputta, imassa moghapurisassa, purā tassa tattheva sattadhā muddhā phalatī’’ ti[ phalissatīti( ka. sī. syā. pī. ka.) aṭṭhakathāsu pana‘‘ phalatīti’’ itveva dissati]."
351235,92,106,53,66,1,59,9,"‘‘ Khamāmahaṃ, bhante, tassa āyasmato sace maṃ so āyasmā evamāha–"
351236,92,106,67,77,1,26,6,‘ khamatu ca me so āyasmā’’’ ti. 
