351238,92,107,2,4,1,17,2,2 . Saupādisesasuttaṃ 
351239,92,108,2,14,1,73,8,12. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
351240,92,108,15,26,1,94,10,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
351241,92,108,27,32,1,40,5,Atha kho āyasmato sāriputtassa etadahosi–
351242,92,108,33,51,1,119,13,"‘‘ atippago kho tāva sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya carituṃ, yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan’’ ti. "
351243,92,108,52,61,1,81,9,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkami; 
351244,92,108,62,68,1,63,6,upasaṅkamitvā tehi aññatitthiyehi paribbājakehi saddhiṃ sammodi. 
351245,92,108,69,75,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
351246,92,109,2,14,1,112,11,Tena kho pana samayena tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi–
351247,92,109,15,40,1,154,18,"‘‘ yo hi koci, āvuso, saupādiseso kālaṃ karoti, sabbo so aparimutto nirayā aparimutto tiracchānayoniyā aparimutto pettivisayā aparimutto apāyaduggativinipātā’’ ti. "
351248,92,109,41,52,1,99,11,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandi nappaṭikkosi. 
351249,92,109,53,57,1,49,4,Anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi–
351250,92,109,58,69,1,56,7,‘‘ bhagavato santike etassa bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānissāmī’’ ti. 
351251,92,109,70,83,1,114,12,Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
351252,92,109,84,90,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
351253,92,109,91,98,1,60,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
351254,92,110,2,14,1,84,9,"‘ ‘ Idhāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ. "
351255,92,110,15,21,1,29,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, etadahosi–"
351256,92,110,22,30,1,45,6,‘ atippago kho tāva sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya carituṃ; 
351257,92,110,31,39,1,73,7,yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan’ ti. 
351258,92,110,40,51,1,77,9,"Atha kho ahaṃ, bhante, yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; "
351259,92,110,52,58,1,64,6,upasaṅkamitvā tehi aññatitthiyehi paribbājakehi saddhiṃ sammodiṃ. 
351260,92,110,59,65,1,59,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃ. 
351261,92,110,66,77,1,112,11,Tena kho pana samayena tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi–
351262,92,110,78,101,1,154,18,"‘ yo hi koci, āvuso, saupādiseso kālaṃ karoti, sabbo so aparimutto nirayā aparimutto tiracchānayoniyā aparimutto pettivisayā aparimutto apāyaduggativinipātā’ ti. "
351263,92,110,102,115,1,96,11,"Atha kho ahaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandiṃ nappaṭikkosiṃ. "
351264,92,110,116,120,1,50,4,Anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamiṃ–
351265,92,110,121,132,1,56,7,‘ bhagavato santike etassa bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānissāmī’’’ ti.
351266,92,111,2,69,1,143,20,"‘ ‘ Ke ca[ keci( syā. pī.), te ca( ka.)], sāriputta, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā bālā abyattā, ke ca[ keci( syā. pī. ka.) a. ni.6.44 pāḷiyā saṃsandetabbaṃ] saupādisesaṃ vā‘ saupādiseso’ ti jānissanti, anupādisesaṃ vā‘ anupādiseso’ ti jānissanti’’!"
351267,92,112,2,20,1,150,15,"‘ ‘ Navayime, sāriputta, puggalā saupādisesā kālaṃ kurumānā parimuttā nirayā parimuttā tiracchānayoniyā parimuttā pettivisayā parimuttā apāyaduggativinipātā. "
351268,92,112,21,23,1,11,2,Katame nava? 
351269,92,112,24,42,1,100,12,"Idha , sāriputta, ekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ paripūrakārī , paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351270,92,112,43,50,1,74,7,So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti. 
351271,92,112,51,70,1,154,15,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta , paṭhamo puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā parimutto tiracchānayoniyā parimutto pettivisayā parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351272,92,113,2,21,1,111,14,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, idhekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ paripūrakārī, paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351273,92,113,22,45,1,168,17,So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti… pe… asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti… pe… sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti… pe… uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī. 
351274,92,113,46,63,1,154,15,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta, pañcamo puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā parimutto tiracchānayoniyā parimutto pettivisayā parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351275,92,114,2,22,1,111,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, idhekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī, paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351276,92,114,23,38,1,122,14,"So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmī hoti, sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti. "
351277,92,114,39,55,1,108,12,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta, chaṭṭho puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā… pe… parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351278,92,115,2,22,1,111,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, idhekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī, paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351279,92,115,23,37,1,105,12,"So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā ekabījī hoti, ekaṃyeva mānusakaṃ bhavaṃ nibbattetvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti. "
351280,92,115,38,55,1,108,12,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta, sattamo puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā… pe… parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351281,92,116,2,22,1,111,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, idhekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī, paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351282,92,116,23,39,1,114,15,"So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā kolaṃkolo hoti, dve vā tīṇi vā kulāni sandhāvitvā saṃsaritvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti. "
351283,92,116,40,56,1,108,12,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta, aṭṭhamo puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā… pe… parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351284,92,117,2,23,1,111,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, idhekacco puggalo sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti, samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī, paññāya mattaso kārī. "
351285,92,117,24,41,1,140,15,"So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sattakkhattuparamo hoti, sattakkhattuparamaṃ deve ca manusse ca sandhāvitvā saṃsaritvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti. "
351286,92,117,42,59,1,153,15,"Ayaṃ, sāriputta, navamo puggalo saupādiseso kālaṃ kurumāno parimutto nirayā parimutto tiracchānayoniyā parimutto pettivisayā parimutto apāyaduggativinipātā."
351287,92,118,2,31,1,143,20,"‘ ‘ Ke ca, sāriputta, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā bālā abyattā, ke ca saupādisesaṃ vā‘ saupādiseso’ ti jānissanti, anupādisesaṃ vā‘ anupādiseso’ ti jānissanti! "
351288,92,118,32,50,1,154,16,"Ime kho, sāriputta, nava puggalā saupādisesā kālaṃ kurumānā parimuttā nirayā parimuttā tiracchānayoniyā parimuttā pettivisayā parimuttā apāyaduggativinipātā. "
