351868,92,267,23,25,1,14,2,Tassā evamassa–
351869,92,267,26,43,1,116,13,"‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ agatapubbañceva disaṃ gaccheyyaṃ, akhāditapubbāni ca tiṇāni khādeyyaṃ, apītapubbāni ca pānīyāni piveyyan’ ti. "
351870,92,267,44,53,1,75,9,Sā purimaṃ pādaṃ na suppatiṭṭhitaṃ patiṭṭhāpetvā pacchimaṃ pādaṃ uddhareyya. 
351871,92,267,54,72,1,112,16,"Sā na ceva agatapubbaṃ disaṃ gaccheyya, na ca akhāditapubbāni tiṇāni khādeyya, na ca apītapubbāni pānīyāni piveyya; "
351872,92,267,73,78,1,36,5,yasmiṃ cassā padese ṭhitāya evamassa–
351873,92,267,79,103,1,157,18,"‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ agatapubbañceva disaṃ gaccheyyaṃ, akhāditapubbāni ca tiṇāni khādeyyaṃ, apītapubbāni ca pānīyāni piveyyan’ ti tañca padesaṃ na sotthinā paccāgaccheyya. "
351874,92,267,104,107,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
351875,92,267,108,123,1,92,13,"Tathā hi sā, bhikkhave, gāvī pabbateyyā bālā abyattā akhettaññū akusalā visame pabbate carituṃ. "
351876,92,267,124,148,1,195,22,"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu bālo abyatto akhettaññū akusalo vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati; "
351877,92,267,149,161,1,81,12,so taṃ nimittaṃ na āsevati na bhāveti na bahulīkaroti na svādhiṭṭhitaṃ adhiṭṭhāti.
351878,92,268,2,7,1,15,4,‘ ‘ Tassa evaṃ hoti–
351879,92,268,8,27,1,160,16,‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ ti. 
351880,92,268,28,40,1,79,10,So na sakkoti vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā… pe… dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ. 
