352200,92,332,2,4,1,13,2,10 . Tapussasuttaṃ 
352201,92,333,2,16,1,72,9,41. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā mallesu viharati uruvelakappaṃ nāma mallānaṃ nigamo. 
352202,92,333,17,26,1,89,9,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya uruvelakappaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
352203,92,333,27,35,1,90,8,Uruvelakappe piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi–
352204,92,333,36,53,1,74,10,"‘‘ idheva tāva tvaṃ, ānanda, hohi, yāvāhaṃ mahāvanaṃ ajjhogāhāmi divāvihārāyā’’ ti."
352205,92,333,54,67,1,53,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho āyasmā ānando bhagavato paccassosi. "
352206,92,333,68,77,1,82,9,Atha kho bhagavā mahāvanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. 
352207,92,334,2,9,1,56,7,Atha kho tapusso gahapati yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; 
352208,92,334,10,16,1,61,6,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
352209,92,334,17,25,1,67,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho tapusso gahapati āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca–
352210,92,335,2,14,1,68,9,"‘ ‘ Mayaṃ, bhante ānanda, gihī kāmabhogino kāmārāmā kāmaratā kāmasammuditā. "
352211,92,335,15,33,1,124,14,"Tesaṃ no, bhante, amhākaṃ gihīnaṃ kāmabhogīnaṃ kāmārāmānaṃ kāmaratānaṃ kāmasammuditānaṃ papāto viya khāyati, yadidaṃ nekkhammaṃ. "
352212,92,335,34,61,1,152,17,"Sutaṃ metaṃ, bhante,‘ imasmiṃ dhammavinaye daharānaṃ daharānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ nekkhamme cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’[ passataṃ(?)]. "
352213,92,335,62,78,1,92,11,"Tayidaṃ, bhante, imasmiṃ dhammavinaye bhikkhūnaṃ bahunā janena visabhāgo, yadidaṃ nekkhamman’’ ti."
352214,92,336,2,14,1,59,8,"‘ ‘ Atthi kho etaṃ, gahapati, kathāpābhataṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. "
352215,92,336,15,22,1,46,5,"Āyāma, gahapati, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamissāma; "
352216,92,336,23,27,1,45,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocessāma. 
352217,92,336,28,38,1,53,8,Yathā no bhagavā byākarissati tathā naṃ dhāressāmā’’ ti.
352218,92,337,2,16,1,65,10,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho tapusso gahapati āyasmato ānandassa paccassosi. "
352219,92,337,17,28,1,78,10,Atha kho āyasmā ānando tapussena gahapatinā saddhiṃ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
352220,92,337,29,34,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
352221,92,337,35,42,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
352222,92,338,2,12,1,36,6,"‘ ‘ Ayaṃ , bhante, tapusso gahapati evamāha–"
352223,92,338,13,42,1,193,22,"‘ mayaṃ, bhante ānanda, gihī kāmabhogino kāmārāmā kāmaratā kāmasammuditā, tesaṃ no bhante, amhākaṃ gihīnaṃ kāmabhogīnaṃ kāmārāmānaṃ kāmaratānaṃ kāmasammuditānaṃ papāto viya khāyati, yadidaṃ nekkhammaṃ’. "
352224,92,338,43,63,1,152,17,"Sutaṃ metaṃ, bhante,‘ imasmiṃ dhammavinaye daharānaṃ daharānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ nekkhamme cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato. "
