352226,92,339,2,11,1,31,5,"‘ ‘ Evametaṃ, ānanda, evametaṃ, ānanda! "
352227,92,339,12,23,1,86,9,"Mayhampi kho, ānanda, pubbeva sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi–"
352228,92,339,24,33,1,34,5,"‘ sādhu nekkhammaṃ , sādhu paviveko’ ti. "
352229,92,339,34,51,1,113,15,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, nekkhamme cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato. "
352230,92,339,52,58,1,29,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi–"
352231,92,339,59,82,1,127,20,"‘ ko nu kho hetu ko paccayo, yena me nekkhamme cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’? "
352232,92,339,83,89,1,29,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi–"
352233,92,339,90,112,1,102,17,"‘ kāmesu kho me ādīnavo adiṭṭho, so ca me abahulīkato, nekkhamme ca ānisaṃso anadhigato, so ca me anāsevito . "
352234,92,339,113,128,1,102,14,Tasmā me nekkhamme cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’. 
352235,92,339,129,135,1,29,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi–"
352236,92,339,136,179,1,219,28,"‘ sace kho ahaṃ kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulaṃ kareyyaṃ[ bahulīkareyyaṃ( sī. syā. pī.)], nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseveyyaṃ, ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati yaṃ me nekkhamme cittaṃ pakkhandeyya pasīdeyya santiṭṭheyya vimucceyya etaṃ santanti passato’. "
352237,92,339,180,198,1,115,15,"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, aparena samayena kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulamakāsiṃ, nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseviṃ. "
352238,92,339,199,213,1,101,12,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, nekkhamme cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato. "
352239,92,339,214,233,1,141,17,"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
352240,92,339,234,245,1,86,9,"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, iminā vihārena viharato kāmasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. "
