352900,93,81,2,25,1,95,14,"39.‘‘ Hoti kho so, bhikkhave, samayo, yaṃ kadāci karahaci dīghassa addhuno accayena ayaṃ loko saṃvaṭṭati. "
352901,93,81,26,32,1,62,6,Saṃvaṭṭamāne loke yebhuyyena sattā ābhassarasaṃvattanikā honti. 
352902,93,81,33,45,1,107,11,"Te tattha honti manomayā pītibhakkhā sayaṃpabhā antalikkhacarā subhaṭṭhāyino, ciraṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ tiṭṭhanti. "
352903,93,82,2,25,1,94,14,"40.‘‘ Hoti kho so, bhikkhave, samayo, yaṃ kadāci karahaci dīghassa addhuno accayena ayaṃ loko vivaṭṭati. "
352904,93,82,26,31,1,49,5,Vivaṭṭamāne loke suññaṃ brahmavimānaṃ pātubhavati. 
352905,93,82,32,46,1,105,13,Atha kho aññataro satto āyukkhayā vā puññakkhayā vā ābhassarakāyā cavitvā suññaṃ brahmavimānaṃ upapajjati. 
352906,93,82,47,60,1,103,11,"So tattha hoti manomayo pītibhakkho sayaṃpabho antalikkhacaro subhaṭṭhāyī, ciraṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ tiṭṭhati. "
352907,93,83,2,16,1,79,8,41.‘‘ Tassa tattha ekakassa dīgharattaṃ nivusitattā anabhirati paritassanā upapajjati–
