352909,93,83,27,41,1,119,14,Atha aññepi sattā āyukkhayā vā puññakkhayā vā ābhassarakāyā cavitvā brahmavimānaṃ upapajjanti tassa sattassa sahabyataṃ. 
352910,93,83,42,54,1,109,11,"Tepi tattha honti manomayā pītibhakkhā sayaṃpabhā antalikkhacarā subhaṭṭhāyino, ciraṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ tiṭṭhanti. "
352911,93,84,2,21,1,61,10,"42.‘‘ Tatra , bhikkhave, yo so satto paṭhamaṃ upapanno tassa evaṃ hoti–"
352912,93,84,22,48,1,131,15,‘ ahamasmi brahmā mahābrahmā abhibhū anabhibhūto aññadatthudaso vasavattī issaro kattā nimmātā seṭṭho sajitā[ sajjitā( syā. kaṃ.)] vasī pitā bhūtabhabyānaṃ. 
352913,93,84,49,53,1,22,4,Mayā ime sattā nimmitā. 
352914,93,84,54,57,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
352915,93,84,58,61,1,23,3,Mamañhi pubbe etadahosi–
