352917,93,84,74,86,1,55,10,"Iti mama ca manopaṇidhi, ime ca sattā itthattaṃ āgatā’ ti."
352918,93,85,2,13,1,47,9,"‘ ‘ Yepi te sattā pacchā upapannā, tesampi evaṃ hoti–"
352919,93,85,14,32,1,138,17,‘ ayaṃ kho bhavaṃ brahmā mahābrahmā abhibhū anabhibhūto aññadatthudaso vasavattī issaro kattā nimmātā seṭṭho sajitā vasī pitā bhūtabhabyānaṃ. 
