352922,93,85,43,56,1,78,11,"Imañhi mayaṃ addasāma idha paṭhamaṃ upapannaṃ, mayaṃ panamha pacchā upapannā’ ti. "
352923,93,86,2,26,1,106,15,"43.‘‘ Tatra, bhikkhave, yo so satto paṭhamaṃ upapanno, so dīghāyukataro ca hoti vaṇṇavantataro ca mahesakkhataro ca. "
352924,93,86,27,42,1,91,14,"Ye pana te sattā pacchā upapannā, te appāyukatarā ca honti dubbaṇṇatarā ca appesakkhatarā ca. "
352925,93,87,2,24,1,94,13,"44.‘‘ Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati, yaṃ aññataro satto tamhā kāyā cavitvā itthattaṃ āgacchati. "
352926,93,87,25,31,1,52,6,Itthattaṃ āgato samāno agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajati. 
