353709,93,313,18,63,1,337,36,"Idha, mahārāja, bhikkhu abhikkante paṭikkante sampajānakārī hoti, ālokite vilokite sampajānakārī hoti, samiñjite pasārite sampajānakārī hoti, saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇe sampajānakārī hoti, asite pīte khāyite sāyite sampajānakārī hoti, uccārapassāvakamme sampajānakārī hoti, gate ṭhite nisinne sutte jāgarite bhāsite tuṇhībhāve sampajānakārī hoti. "
353710,93,313,64,74,1,59,7,"Evaṃ kho, mahārāja , bhikkhu satisampajaññena samannāgato hoti. "
353711,93,314,2,2,1,7,1,Santoso 
353712,93,315,2,15,1,40,5,"215.‘‘ Kathañca, mahārāja, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti? "
353713,93,315,16,29,1,93,9,"Idha, mahārāja, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti kāyaparihārikena cīvarena, kucchiparihārikena piṇḍapātena . "
353714,93,315,30,37,1,45,6,"So yena yeneva pakkamati, samādāyeva pakkamati. "
353715,93,315,38,50,1,70,9,"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, pakkhī sakuṇo yena yeneva ḍeti, sapattabhārova ḍeti. "
353716,93,315,51,63,1,100,10,"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti kāyaparihārikena cīvarena kucchiparihārikena piṇḍapātena. "
353717,93,315,64,71,1,45,6,"So yena yeneva pakkamati, samādāyeva pakkamati. "
353718,93,315,72,80,1,40,6,"Evaṃ kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti. "
353719,93,316,2,2,1,16,1,Nīvaraṇappahānaṃ 
353720,93,317,2,45,1,298,33,"216.‘‘ So iminā ca ariyena sīlakkhandhena samannāgato, iminā ca ariyena indriyasaṃvarena samannāgato, iminā ca ariyena satisampajaññena samannāgato, imāya ca ariyāya santuṭṭhiyā samannāgato, vivittaṃ senāsanaṃ bhajati araññaṃ rukkhamūlaṃ pabbataṃ kandaraṃ giriguhaṃ susānaṃ vanapatthaṃ abbhokāsaṃ palālapuñjaṃ. "
353721,93,317,46,58,1,117,12,So pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātappaṭikkanto nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. 
353722,93,318,2,19,1,86,10,"217.‘‘ So abhijjhaṃ loke pahāya vigatābhijjhena cetasā viharati, abhijjhāya cittaṃ parisodheti. "
353723,93,318,20,30,1,104,8,"Byāpādapadosaṃ pahāya abyāpannacitto viharati sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī, byāpādapadosā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
353724,93,318,31,43,1,103,10,"Thinamiddhaṃ pahāya vigatathinamiddho viharati ālokasaññī, sato sampajāno, thinamiddhā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
353725,93,318,44,55,1,104,9,"Uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahāya anuddhato viharati, ajjhattaṃ vūpasantacitto, uddhaccakukkuccā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
353726,93,318,56,68,1,106,10,"Vicikicchaṃ pahāya tiṇṇavicikiccho viharati, akathaṃkathī kusalesu dhammesu, vicikicchāya cittaṃ parisodheti. "
353727,93,319,2,18,1,56,7,"218.‘‘ Seyyathāpi , mahārāja, puriso iṇaṃ ādāya kammante payojeyya. "
353728,93,319,19,23,1,30,4,Tassa te kammantā samijjheyyuṃ. 
353729,93,319,24,51,1,97,14,"So yāni ca porāṇāni iṇamūlāni, tāni ca byantiṃ kareyya[ byantīkareyya( sī. syā. kaṃ.)], siyā cassa uttariṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ dārabharaṇāya. "
353730,93,319,52,54,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353731,93,319,55,64,1,44,7,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe iṇaṃ ādāya kammante payojesiṃ. 
353732,93,319,65,71,1,32,5,Tassa me te kammantā samijjhiṃsu. 
353733,93,319,72,91,1,103,16,"Sohaṃ yāni ca porāṇāni iṇamūlāni, tāni ca byantiṃ akāsiṃ, atthi ca me uttariṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ dārabharaṇāyā’ ti. "
353734,93,319,92,99,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
353735,93,320,2,17,1,61,7,"219.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso ābādhiko assa dukkhito bāḷhagilāno; "
353736,93,320,18,25,1,48,6,"bhattañcassa nacchādeyya, na cassa kāye balamattā. "
353737,93,320,26,32,1,41,6,So aparena samayena tamhā ābādhā mucceyya; 
353738,93,320,33,41,1,48,7,"bhattaṃ cassa chādeyya, siyā cassa kāye balamattā. "
353739,93,320,42,44,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353740,93,320,45,53,1,51,7,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe ābādhiko ahosiṃ dukkhito bāḷhagilāno; 
353741,93,320,54,73,1,51,9,"bhattañca me nacchādesi, na ca me āsi[ na cassa me( ka.)] kāye balamattā. "
353742,93,320,74,79,1,32,5,Somhi etarahi tamhā ābādhā mutto; 
353743,93,320,80,91,1,50,9,"bhattañca me chādeti, atthi ca me kāye balamattā’ ti. "
353744,93,320,92,99,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
353745,93,321,2,16,1,51,6,"220.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso bandhanāgāre baddho assa. "
353746,93,321,17,40,1,95,13,"So aparena samayena tamhā bandhanāgārā mucceyya sotthinā abbhayena[ ubbayena( sī. ka.)], na cassa kiñci bhogānaṃ vayo. "
353747,93,321,41,43,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353748,93,321,44,60,1,99,13,"‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe bandhanāgāre baddho ahosiṃ, somhi etarahi tamhā bandhanāgārā mutto sotthinā abbhayena. "
353749,93,321,61,70,1,35,7,Natthi ca me kiñci bhogānaṃ vayo’ ti. 
353750,93,321,71,78,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
353751,93,322,2,19,1,75,9,"221.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso dāso assa anattādhīno parādhīno na yenakāmaṃgamo. "
353752,93,322,20,30,1,86,10,So aparena samayena tamhā dāsabyā mucceyya attādhīno aparādhīno bhujisso yenakāmaṃgamo. 
353753,93,322,31,33,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353754,93,322,34,44,1,65,9,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe dāso ahosiṃ anattādhīno parādhīno na yenakāmaṃgamo. 
353755,93,322,45,56,1,80,10,Somhi etarahi tamhā dāsabyā mutto attādhīno aparādhīno bhujisso yenakāmaṃgamo’ ti. 
353756,93,322,57,65,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
353757,93,323,2,19,1,101,9,"222.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso sadhano sabhogo kantāraddhānamaggaṃ paṭipajjeyya dubbhikkhaṃ sappaṭibhayaṃ. "
353758,93,323,20,32,1,95,11,"So aparena samayena taṃ kantāraṃ nitthareyya sotthinā, gāmantaṃ anupāpuṇeyya khemaṃ appaṭibhayaṃ. "
353759,93,323,33,35,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353760,93,323,36,46,1,87,9,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe sadhano sabhogo kantāraddhānamaggaṃ paṭipajjiṃ dubbhikkhaṃ sappaṭibhayaṃ. 
353761,93,323,47,60,1,87,11,"Somhi etarahi taṃ kantāraṃ nitthiṇṇo sotthinā, gāmantaṃ anuppatto khemaṃ appaṭibhayan’ ti. "
353762,93,323,61,68,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
353763,93,324,2,33,1,166,21,"223.‘‘ Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu yathā iṇaṃ yathā rogaṃ yathā bandhanāgāraṃ yathā dāsabyaṃ yathā kantāraddhānamaggaṃ, evaṃ ime pañca nīvaraṇe appahīne attani samanupassati. "
353764,93,325,2,22,1,106,12,"224.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, yathā āṇaṇyaṃ yathā ārogyaṃ yathā bandhanāmokkhaṃ yathā bhujissaṃ yathā khemantabhūmiṃ; "
353765,93,325,23,35,1,75,10,"evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu ime pañca nīvaraṇe pahīne attani samanupassati. "
353766,93,326,2,33,1,174,20,"225.‘‘ Tassime pañca nīvaraṇe pahīne attani samanupassato pāmojjaṃ jāyati, pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vedeti, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
353767,93,327,2,2,1,14,1,Paṭhamajjhānaṃ 
353768,93,328,2,23,1,125,14,"226.‘‘ So vivicceva kāmehi, vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
353769,93,328,24,43,1,154,17,"So imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353770,93,329,2,37,1,223,24,"227.‘‘ Seyyathāpi , mahārāja, dakkho nhāpako vā nhāpakantevāsī vā kaṃsathāle nhānīyacuṇṇāni ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ paripphosakaṃ sanneyya, sāyaṃ nhānīyapiṇḍi snehānugatā snehaparetā santarabāhirā phuṭā snehena, na ca paggharaṇī; "
353771,93,329,38,61,1,180,20,"evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353772,93,329,62,74,1,116,10,"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
353773,93,330,2,2,1,13,1,Dutiyajjhānaṃ 
353774,93,331,2,29,1,174,18,"228.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, mahārāja, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
353775,93,331,30,49,1,156,17,"So imameva kāyaṃ samādhijena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa samādhijena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353776,93,332,2,57,1,274,32,"229.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, udakarahado gambhīro ubbhidodako[ ubbhitodako( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] tassa nevassa puratthimāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, na dakkhiṇāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, na pacchimāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, na uttarāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, devo ca na kālenakālaṃ sammādhāraṃ anuppaveccheyya. "
353777,93,332,58,82,1,206,23,"Atha kho tamhāva udakarahadā sītā vāridhārā ubbhijjitvā tameva udakarahadaṃ sītena vārinā abhisandeyya parisandeyya paripūreyya paripphareyya, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato udakarahadassa sītena vārinā apphuṭaṃ assa. "
353778,93,332,83,108,1,182,20,"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ samādhijena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa samādhijena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353779,93,332,109,121,1,116,10,"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
353780,93,333,2,2,1,13,1,Tatiyajjhānaṃ 
353781,93,334,2,31,1,138,19,"230.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, mahārāja, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati sato sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti–"
353782,93,334,32,43,1,67,8,"‘ upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ ti, tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
353783,93,334,44,62,1,148,17,"So imameva kāyaṃ nippītikena sukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa nippītikena sukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353784,93,335,2,74,1,366,46,"231.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, uppaliniyaṃ vā paduminiyaṃ vā puṇḍarīkiniyaṃ vā appekaccāni uppalāni vā padumāni vā puṇḍarīkāni vā udake jātāni udake saṃvaḍḍhāni udakānuggatāni antonimuggaposīni, tāni yāva caggā yāva ca mūlā sītena vārinā abhisannāni parisannāni[ abhisandāni parisandāni( ka.)] paripūrāni paripphuṭāni[ paripphuṭṭhāni( pī.)], nāssa kiñci sabbāvataṃ uppalānaṃ vā padumānaṃ vā puṇḍarīkānaṃ vā sītena vārinā apphuṭaṃ assa; "
353785,93,335,75,98,1,174,20,"evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ nippītikena sukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa nippītikena sukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
353786,93,335,99,112,1,116,10,"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
353787,93,336,2,2,1,15,1,Catutthajjhānaṃ 
353788,93,337,2,51,1,335,37,"232.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, mahārāja, bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā, pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati, so imameva kāyaṃ parisuddhena cetasā pariyodātena pharitvā nisinno hoti, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa parisuddhena cetasā pariyodātena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
