353792,93,339,2,2,1,14,1,Vipassanāñāṇaṃ 
353793,93,340,2,35,1,156,16,234.‘‘ So[ puna caparaṃ mahārāja bhikkhu so( ka.)] evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti. 
353794,93,340,36,39,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
353795,93,340,40,50,1,126,9,‘ ayaṃ kho me kāyo rūpī cātumahābhūtiko mātāpettikasambhavo odanakummāsūpacayo aniccucchādana-parimaddana-bhedana-viddhaṃsana-dhammo; 
353796,93,340,51,61,1,56,9,idañca pana me viññāṇaṃ ettha sitaṃ ettha paṭibaddhan’ ti. 
353797,93,341,2,22,1,114,12,"235.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, maṇi veḷuriyo subho jātimā aṭṭhaṃso suparikammakato accho vippasanno anāvilo sabbākārasampanno. "
353798,93,341,23,46,1,76,13,Tatrāssa suttaṃ āvutaṃ nīlaṃ vā pītaṃ vā lohitaṃ vā[ pītakaṃ vā lohitakaṃ vā( ka.)] odātaṃ vā paṇḍusuttaṃ vā. 
353799,93,341,47,53,1,53,6,Tamenaṃ cakkhumā puriso hatthe karitvā paccavekkheyya–
353800,93,341,54,67,1,103,12,‘ ayaṃ kho maṇi veḷuriyo subho jātimā aṭṭhaṃso suparikammakato accho vippasanno anāvilo sabbākārasampanno; 
353801,93,341,68,84,1,79,14,tatridaṃ suttaṃ āvutaṃ nīlaṃ vā pītaṃ vā lohitaṃ vā odātaṃ vā paṇḍusuttaṃ vā’ ti. 
353802,93,341,85,106,1,182,19,"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti. "
353803,93,341,107,110,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
353804,93,341,111,121,1,126,9,‘ ayaṃ kho me kāyo rūpī cātumahābhūtiko mātāpettikasambhavo odanakummāsūpacayo aniccucchādanaparimaddanabhedanaviddhaṃsanadhammo; 
353805,93,341,122,133,1,56,9,idañca pana me viññāṇaṃ ettha sitaṃ ettha paṭibaddhan’ ti. 
