353807,93,342,2,2,1,17,1,Manomayiddhiñāṇaṃ 
353808,93,343,2,27,1,172,18,236.‘‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte manomayaṃ kāyaṃ abhinimmānāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti. 
353809,93,343,28,38,1,87,10,So imamhā kāyā aññaṃ kāyaṃ abhinimmināti rūpiṃ manomayaṃ sabbaṅgapaccaṅgiṃ ahīnindriyaṃ. 
353810,93,344,2,25,1,52,6,"237.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso muñjamhā īsikaṃ pavāheyya[ pabbāheyya( syā. ka.)]. "
353811,93,344,26,28,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353812,93,344,29,57,1,75,13,"‘ ayaṃ muñjo, ayaṃ īsikā, añño muñjo, aññā īsikā, muñjamhā tveva īsikā pavāḷhā’ ti[ pabbāḷhāti( syā. ka.)]. "
353813,93,344,58,68,1,54,8,"Seyyathā vā pana, mahārāja, puriso asiṃ kosiyā pavāheyya. "
353814,93,344,69,71,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353815,93,344,72,92,1,65,13,"‘ ayaṃ asi, ayaṃ kosi, añño asi, aññā kosi, kosiyā tveva asi pavāḷho’’ ti. "
353816,93,344,93,103,1,56,8,"Seyyathā vā pana, mahārāja, puriso ahiṃ karaṇḍā uddhareyya. "
353817,93,344,104,106,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
353818,93,344,107,113,1,21,4,"‘ ayaṃ ahi, ayaṃ karaṇḍo. "
