353989,93,382,2,2,1,16,1,Paṭhamaibbhavādo 
353990,93,383,2,14,1,19,4,"263.‘‘ No hidaṃ, bho gotama. "
353991,93,383,15,66,1,321,40,"Gacchanto vā hi, bho gotama, gacchantena brāhmaṇo brāhmaṇena saddhiṃ sallapitumarahati, ṭhito vā hi, bho gotama, ṭhitena brāhmaṇo brāhmaṇena saddhiṃ sallapitumarahati, nisinno vā hi, bho gotama, nisinnena brāhmaṇo brāhmaṇena saddhiṃ sallapitumarahati, sayāno vā hi, bho gotama, sayānena brāhmaṇo brāhmaṇena saddhiṃ sallapitumarahati. "
353992,93,383,67,105,1,137,21,"Ye ca kho te, bho gotama, muṇḍakā samaṇakā ibbhā kaṇhā[ kiṇhā( ka. sī. pī.)] bandhupādāpaccā, tehipi me saddhiṃ evaṃ kathāsallāpo hoti, yathariva bhotā gotamenā’’ ti."
353993,93,383,106,146,1,127,16,"‘‘ Atthikavato kho pana te, ambaṭṭha, idhāgamanaṃ ahosi, yāyeva kho panatthāya āgaccheyyātha[ āgaccheyyātho( sī. pī.)], tameva atthaṃ sādhukaṃ manasi kareyyātha[ manasikareyyātho( sī. pī.)]. "
353994,93,383,147,160,1,83,11,Avusitavāyeva kho pana bho ayaṃ ambaṭṭho māṇavo vusitamānī kimaññatra avusitattā’’ ti. 
353995,93,384,2,21,1,156,15,264. Atha kho ambaṭṭho māṇavo bhagavatā avusitavādena vuccamāno kupito anattamano bhagavantaṃyeva khuṃsento bhagavantaṃyeva vambhento bhagavantaṃyeva upavadamāno–
353996,93,384,22,38,1,66,10,"‘‘ samaṇo ca me, bho, gotamo pāpito bhavissatī’’ ti bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
353997,93,384,39,47,1,26,4,"‘‘ caṇḍā, bho gotama, sakyajāti; "
353998,93,384,48,54,1,28,4,"pharusā, bho gotama, sakyajāti; "
353999,93,384,55,63,1,27,4,"lahusā, bho gotama, sakyajāti; "
354000,93,384,64,70,1,27,4,"bhassā, bho gotama, sakyajāti; "
354001,93,384,71,109,1,136,20,"ibbhā santā ibbhā samānā na brāhmaṇe sakkaronti, na brāhmaṇe garuṃ karonti[ garukaronti( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], na brāhmaṇe mānenti, na brāhmaṇe pūjenti, na brāhmaṇe apacāyanti. "
354002,93,384,110,149,1,203,29,"Tayidaṃ, bho gotama, nacchannaṃ, tayidaṃ nappatirūpaṃ, yadime sakyā ibbhā santā ibbhā samānā na brāhmaṇe sakkaronti, na brāhmaṇe garuṃ karonti, na brāhmaṇe mānenti, na brāhmaṇe pūjenti, na brāhmaṇe apacāyantī’’ ti. "
