354349,93,467,114,152,1,194,28,"Tattha ye te māṇavakā vā māṇavikā vā bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ abhivādessanti vā paccuṭṭhissanti[ paccuṭṭhassanti( pī.)] vā āsanaṃ vā udakaṃ vā dassanti cittaṃ vā pasādessanti, tesaṃ taṃ bhavissati dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’’ ti."
354350,93,467,153,162,1,28,4,"‘‘ Kalyāṇaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇā’’ ti. "
354351,93,468,2,5,1,32,3,Ambaṭṭhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ tatiyaṃ. 
354352,93,469,2,5,1,15,1,4. Soṇadaṇḍasuttaṃ 
354353,93,470,2,2,1,28,1,Campeyyakabrāhmaṇagahapatikā 
354354,93,471,2,28,1,138,17,300. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā aṅgesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi yena campā tadavasari. 
354355,93,471,29,37,1,65,8,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre. 
354356,93,471,38,57,1,179,19,Tena kho pana samayena soṇadaṇḍo brāhmaṇo campaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā māgadhena seniyena bimbisārena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ. 
354357,93,472,2,10,1,41,4,301. Assosuṃ kho campeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
354358,93,472,11,35,1,199,22,‘‘ samaṇo khalu bho gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito aṅgesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi campaṃ anuppatto campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre. 
354359,93,472,36,45,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
354360,93,472,46,63,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
354361,93,472,64,77,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
354362,93,472,78,90,1,135,12,So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. 
354363,93,472,91,102,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
354364,93,472,103,128,1,122,12,Atha kho campeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā campāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī[ saṅghā saṅghī( sī. syā. pī.)] gaṇībhūtā yena gaggarā pokkharaṇī tenupasaṅkamanti. 
354365,93,473,2,16,1,77,10,302. Tena kho pana samayena soṇadaṇḍo brāhmaṇo uparipāsāde divāseyyaṃ upagato hoti. 
354366,93,473,17,48,1,143,14,Addasā kho soṇadaṇḍo brāhmaṇo campeyyake brāhmaṇagahapatike campāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī [ saṅghe saṅghī( sī. pī.) saṅghā saṅghī( syā.)] gaṇībhūte yena gaggarā pokkharaṇī tenupasaṅkamante. 
354367,93,473,49,52,1,22,3,Disvā khattaṃ āmantesi–
354368,93,473,53,76,1,138,16,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bho khatte, campeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā campāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā yena gaggarā pokkharaṇī tenupasaṅkamantī’’ ti?"
354369,93,473,77,104,1,203,23,"‘‘ Atthi kho, bho, samaṇo gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito aṅgesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi campaṃ anuppatto campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre. "
354370,93,473,105,114,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
354371,93,473,115,132,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
354372,93,473,133,141,1,51,6,Tamete bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamantī’’ ti.
354373,93,473,142,160,1,123,13,"‘‘ Tena hi, bho khatte, yena campeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkama, upasaṅkamitvā campeyyake brāhmaṇagahapatike evaṃ vadehi–"
354374,93,473,161,183,1,119,14,"‘ soṇadaṇḍo, bho, brāhmaṇo evamāha– āgamentu kira bhavanto, soṇadaṇḍopi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’’ ti."
354375,93,473,184,203,1,110,13,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho so khattā soṇadaṇḍassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena campeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkami; "
354376,93,473,204,208,1,53,4,upasaṅkamitvā campeyyake brāhmaṇagahapatike etadavoca–
