354378,93,473,217,232,1,88,10,"‘ āgamentu kira bhavanto, soṇadaṇḍopi brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’’ ti. "
354379,93,474,2,2,1,18,1,Soṇadaṇḍaguṇakathā 
354380,93,475,2,18,1,122,12,303. Tena kho pana samayena nānāverajjakānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ pañcamattāni brāhmaṇasatāni campāyaṃ paṭivasanti kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
354381,93,475,19,23,1,23,4,Assosuṃ kho te brāhmaṇā–
354382,93,475,24,36,1,68,8,‘‘ soṇadaṇḍo kira brāhmaṇo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’ ti. 
