354386,93,475,65,74,1,20,5,"‘‘ Evaṃ kho me, bho, hoti–"
354387,93,475,75,85,1,51,6,‘ ahampi samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāmī’’’ ti.
354388,93,476,2,11,1,56,8,‘ ‘ Mā bhavaṃ soṇadaṇḍo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkami. 
354389,93,476,12,20,1,67,8,Na arahati bhavaṃ soṇadaṇḍo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ. 
354390,93,476,21,39,1,138,15,"Sace bhavaṃ soṇadaṇḍo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissati, bhoto soṇadaṇḍassa yaso hāyissati, samaṇassa gotamassa yaso abhivaḍḍhissati. "
354391,93,476,40,61,1,161,18,"Yampi bhoto soṇadaṇḍassa yaso hāyissati, samaṇassa gotamassa yaso abhivaḍḍhissati , imināpaṅgena na arahati bhavaṃ soṇadaṇḍo samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamituṃ; "
