354455,93,518,95,114,1,99,16,"Ettake kho ahaṃ, bho, tassa bhoto gotamassa vaṇṇe pariyāpuṇāmi, no ca kho so bhavaṃ gotamo ettakavaṇṇo. "
354456,93,518,115,123,1,37,6,Aparimāṇavaṇṇo hi so bhavaṃ gotamo’’ ti. 
