354987,93,654,2,2,1,26,1,Sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyā 
354988,93,655,2,20,1,112,12,"355. Atha kho bhagavā kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi, seyyathidaṃ, dānakathaṃ sīlakathaṃ saggakathaṃ; "
354989,93,655,21,29,1,63,7,kāmānaṃ ādīnavaṃ okāraṃ saṃkilesaṃ nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsesi. 
354990,93,655,30,54,1,198,21,"Yadā bhagavā aññāsi kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ kallacittaṃ muducittaṃ vinīvaraṇacittaṃ udaggacittaṃ pasannacittaṃ, atha yā buddhānaṃ sāmukkaṃsikā dhammadesanā, taṃ pakāsesi– dukkhaṃ samudayaṃ nirodhaṃ maggaṃ. "
354991,93,655,55,74,1,168,17,"Seyyathāpi nāma suddhaṃ vatthaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sammadeva rajanaṃ paṭiggaṇheyya, evameva kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa tasmiññeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi–"
354992,93,655,75,87,1,54,7,"‘‘ yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman’’ ti. "
354993,93,656,2,21,1,182,15,356. Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo pariyogāḷhadhammo tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṃkatho vesārajjappatto aparappaccayo satthusāsane bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
