354995,93,656,36,39,1,31,3,Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. 
354996,93,657,2,19,1,119,13,357. Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
354997,93,657,20,36,1,135,16,Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo tassā rattiyā accayena sake yaññavāṭe paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā bhagavato kālaṃ ārocāpesi–
354998,93,657,37,43,1,15,3,"‘‘ kālo, bho gotama; "
354999,93,657,44,49,1,20,3,niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan’’ ti. 
