355761,93,826,2,3,1,18,2,Tayo attapaṭilābhā 
355762,93,827,2,24,1,101,11,"428.‘‘ Tayo kho me, poṭṭhapāda, attapaṭilābhā– oḷāriko attapaṭilābho, manomayo attapaṭilābho, arūpo attapaṭilābho. "
355763,93,827,25,32,1,42,5,"Katamo ca, poṭṭhapāda, oḷāriko attapaṭilābho? "
355764,93,827,33,49,1,69,6,"Rūpī cātumahābhūtiko kabaḷīkārāhārabhakkho[ kabaḷīkārabhakkho( syā. ka.)], ayaṃ oḷāriko attapaṭilābho. "
355765,93,827,50,53,1,29,3,Katamo manomayo attapaṭilābho? 
355766,93,827,54,62,1,70,7,"Rūpī manomayo sabbaṅgapaccaṅgī ahīnindriyo, ayaṃ manomayo attapaṭilābho. "
355767,93,827,63,66,1,26,3,Katamo arūpo attapaṭilābho? 
355768,93,827,67,73,1,40,5,"Arūpī saññāmayo, ayaṃ arūpo attapaṭilābho. "
355769,93,828,2,40,1,257,25,"429.‘‘ Oḷārikassapi kho ahaṃ, poṭṭhapāda, attapaṭilābhassa pahānāya dhammaṃ desemi– yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṃkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathāti. "
355770,93,828,41,82,1,261,31,"Siyā kho pana te, poṭṭhapāda, evamassa– saṃkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissati, dukkho ca kho vihāroti, na kho panetaṃ, poṭṭhapāda, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
355771,93,828,83,116,1,251,30,"Saṃkilesikā ceva dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā ca dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissati, pāmujjaṃ ceva bhavissati pīti ca passaddhi ca sati ca sampajaññañca sukho ca vihāro. "
355772,93,829,2,38,1,258,25,"430.‘‘ Manomayassapi kho ahaṃ, poṭṭhapāda, attapaṭilābhassa pahānāya dhammaṃ desemi yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṃkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathāti . "
355773,93,829,39,47,1,36,6,"Siyā kho pana te, poṭṭhapāda, evamassa–"
