355780,93,831,2,16,1,39,6,"432.‘‘ Pare ce, poṭṭhapāda, amhe evaṃ puccheyyuṃ–"
355781,93,831,17,62,1,306,35,"‘ katamo pana so, āvuso , oḷāriko attapaṭilābho, yassa tumhe pahānāya dhammaṃ desetha, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṃkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ ti, tesaṃ mayaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākareyyāma–"
