355877,93,852,2,5,1,11,1,10. Subhasuttaṃ 
355878,93,853,2,2,1,17,1,Subhamāṇavavatthu 
355879,93,854,2,25,1,120,14,444. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme aciraparinibbute bhagavati. 
355880,93,854,26,37,1,93,11,Tena kho pana samayena subho māṇavo todeyyaputto sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati kenacideva karaṇīyena. 
355881,93,855,2,14,1,63,8,445. Atha kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto aññataraṃ māṇavakaṃ āmantesi–
355882,93,855,15,26,1,50,7,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, māṇavaka, yena samaṇo ānando tenupasaṅkama; "
355883,93,855,27,38,1,103,11,upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena samaṇaṃ ānandaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ puccha–
355884,93,855,39,53,1,108,12,‘ subho māṇavo todeyyaputto bhavantaṃ ānandaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchatī’ ti. 
355885,93,855,54,56,1,13,2,Evañca vadehi–
355886,93,855,57,74,1,111,13,‘ sādhu kira bhavaṃ ānando yena subhassa māṇavassa todeyyaputtassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’’ ti. 
355887,93,856,2,24,1,104,13,"446.‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho so māṇavako subhassa māṇavassa todeyyaputtassa paṭissutvā yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; "
355888,93,856,25,30,1,47,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodi. 
355889,93,856,31,37,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
355890,93,856,38,46,1,62,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so māṇavako āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca–
355891,93,856,47,60,1,105,11,‘‘ subho māṇavo todeyyaputto bhavantaṃ ānandaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati; 
355892,93,856,61,63,1,13,2,evañca vadeti–
355893,93,856,64,83,1,111,13,‘ sādhu kira bhavaṃ ānando yena subhassa māṇavassa todeyyaputtassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’’ ti. 
355894,93,857,2,14,1,48,7,"447. Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando taṃ māṇavakaṃ etadavoca–"
355895,93,857,15,22,1,18,3,"‘‘ akālo kho, māṇavaka . "
355896,93,857,23,28,1,32,5,Atthi me ajja bhesajjamattā pītā. 
355897,93,857,29,38,1,61,7,Appevanāma svepi upasaṅkameyyāma kālañca samayañca upādāyā’’ ti.
355898,93,858,2,23,1,114,16,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho so māṇavako āyasmato ānandassa paṭissutvā uṭṭhāyāsanā yena subho māṇavo todeyyaputto tenupasaṅkami ; "
355899,93,858,24,40,1,108,13,"upasaṅkamitvā subhaṃ māṇavaṃ todeyyaputtaṃ etadavoca,‘‘ avocumhā kho mayaṃ bhoto vacanena taṃ bhavantaṃ ānandaṃ–"
355900,93,858,41,56,1,119,13,"‘ subho māṇavo todeyyaputto bhavantaṃ ānandaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati, evañca vadeti–"
355901,93,858,57,75,1,111,13,‘‘ sādhu kira bhavaṃ ānando yena subhassa māṇavassa todeyyaputtassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’’ ti. 
355902,93,858,76,85,1,42,7,"Evaṃ vutte, bho, samaṇo ānando maṃ etadavoca–"
355903,93,858,86,91,1,18,3,"‘ akālo kho, māṇavaka. "
355904,93,858,92,97,1,32,5,Atthi me ajja bhesajjamattā pītā. 
355905,93,858,98,106,1,61,7,Appevanāma svepi upasaṅkameyyāma kālañca samayañca upādāyā’ ti. 
355906,93,858,107,126,1,100,14,"Ettāvatāpi kho, bho, katameva etaṃ, yato kho so bhavaṃ ānando okāsamakāsi svātanāyapi upasaṅkamanāyā’’ ti. "
355907,93,859,2,25,1,187,19,448. Atha kho āyasmā ānando tassā rattiyā accayena pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya cetakena bhikkhunā pacchāsamaṇena yena subhassa māṇavassa todeyyaputtassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; 
355908,93,859,26,30,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
355909,93,860,2,11,1,65,8,Atha kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; 
355910,93,860,12,17,1,47,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodi. 
355911,93,860,18,24,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
355912,93,860,25,34,1,76,9,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho subho māṇavo todeyyaputto āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca–
355913,93,860,35,47,1,84,9,‘‘ bhavañhi ānando tassa bhoto gotamassa dīgharattaṃ upaṭṭhāko santikāvacaro samīpacārī. 
355914,93,860,48,67,1,130,17,"Bhavametaṃ ānando jāneyya, yesaṃ so bhavaṃ gotamo dhammānaṃ vaṇṇavādī ahosi, yattha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesi. "
355915,93,860,68,80,1,69,10,"Katamesānaṃ kho, bho ānanda, dhammānaṃ so bhavaṃ gotamo vaṇṇavādī ahosi; "
355916,93,860,81,91,1,58,8,kattha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesī’’ ti? 
355917,93,861,2,18,1,55,8,"449.‘‘ Tiṇṇaṃ kho, māṇava, khandhānaṃ so bhagavā vaṇṇavādī ahosi; "
355918,93,861,19,26,1,54,7,ettha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesi. 
355919,93,861,27,29,1,16,2,Katamesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ? 
355920,93,861,30,38,1,78,6,"Ariyassa sīlakkhandhassa, ariyassa samādhikkhandhassa, ariyassa paññākkhandhassa. "
355921,93,861,39,50,1,62,9,"Imesaṃ kho, māṇava, tiṇṇaṃ khandhānaṃ so bhagavā vaṇṇavādī ahosi; "
355922,93,861,51,61,1,57,8,ettha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesī’’ ti. 
355923,93,862,2,2,1,12,1,Sīlakkhandho 
355924,93,863,2,37,1,142,21,"450.‘‘ Katamo pana so, bho ānanda, ariyo sīlakkhandho, yassa so bhavaṃ gotamo vaṇṇavādī ahosi, yattha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesī’’ ti?"
355925,93,864,2,22,1,159,17,"‘ ‘ Idha, māṇava, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā. "
355926,93,864,23,36,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
355927,93,864,37,49,1,135,12,So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. 
355928,93,864,50,62,1,78,11,Taṃ dhammaṃ suṇāti gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā aññatarasmiṃ vā kule paccājāto. 
355929,93,864,63,70,1,50,7,So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā tathāgate saddhaṃ paṭilabhati. 
355930,93,864,71,77,1,57,6,So tena saddhāpaṭilābhena samannāgato iti paṭisañcikkhati–
355931,93,864,78,95,1,154,14,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajopatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā, nayidaṃ sukaraṃ agāraṃ ajjhāvasatā ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ saṅkhalikhitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ. "
355932,93,864,96,107,1,94,10,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajeyyan’ ti. 
355933,93,864,108,135,1,228,27,So aparena samayena appaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ pahāya mahantaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ pahāya appaṃ vā ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ pahāya mahantaṃ vā ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ pahāya kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajati. 
355934,93,864,136,168,1,271,23,"So evaṃ pabbajito samāno pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati, ācāragocarasampanno, anumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu, kāyakammavacīkammena samannāgato kusalena, parisuddhājīvo, sīlasampanno, indriyesu guttadvāro, satisampajaññena samannāgato, santuṭṭho. "
355935,93,865,2,15,1,41,5,"451.‘‘ Kathañca, māṇava, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti? "
355936,93,865,16,34,1,141,14,"Idha, māṇava, bhikkhu pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno, sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati. "
355937,93,865,35,55,1,142,14,"Yampi, māṇava, bhikkhu pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno, sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati; "
355938,93,865,56,69,1,23,3,idampissa hoti sīlasmiṃ.( Yathā194 yāva210 anucchedesu evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ).
355939,93,866,2,58,1,548,52,"‘ ‘ Yathā vā paneke bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā saddhādeyyāni bhojanāni bhuñjitvā te evarūpāya tiracchānavijjāya micchājīvena jīvitaṃ kappenti, seyyathidaṃ– santikammaṃ paṇidhikammaṃ bhūtakammaṃ bhūrikammaṃ vassakammaṃ vossakammaṃ vatthukammaṃ vatthuparikammaṃ ācamanaṃ nhāpanaṃ juhanaṃ vamanaṃ virecanaṃ uddhaṃvirecanaṃ adhovirecanaṃ sīsavirecanaṃ kaṇṇatelaṃ nettatappanaṃ natthukammaṃ añjanaṃ paccañjanaṃ sālākiyaṃ sallakattiyaṃ dārakatikicchā mūlabhesajjānaṃ anuppadānaṃ osadhīnaṃ paṭimokkho iti vā iti evarūpāya tiracchānavijjāya micchājīvā paṭivirato hoti. "
355940,93,866,59,96,1,281,31,"Yampi, māṇava, bhikkhu yathā vā paneke bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā saddhādeyyāni bhojanāni bhuñjitvā te evarūpāya tiracchānavijjāya micchājīvena jīvitaṃ kappenti, seyyathidaṃ, santikammaṃ paṇidhikammaṃ… pe… osadhīnaṃ paṭimokkho iti vā iti evarūpāya tiracchānavijjāya micchājīvā paṭivirato hoti. "
355941,93,866,97,100,1,23,3,Idampissa hoti sīlasmiṃ. 
355942,93,867,2,33,1,95,13,"452.‘‘ Sa kho so[ ayaṃ kho so( ka.)], māṇava, bhikkhu evaṃ sīlasampanno na kutoci bhayaṃ samanupassati, yadidaṃ sīlasaṃvarato. "
355943,93,867,34,49,1,115,12,"Seyyathāpi, māṇava, rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto nihatapaccāmitto na kutoci bhayaṃ samanupassati, yadidaṃ paccatthikato. "
355944,93,867,50,65,1,97,12,"Evameva kho, māṇava, bhikkhu evaṃ sīlasampanno na kutoci bhayaṃ samanupassati, yadidaṃ sīlasaṃvarato. "
355945,93,867,66,75,1,82,8,So iminā ariyena sīlakkhandhena samannāgato ajjhattaṃ anavajjasukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. 
355946,93,867,76,84,1,41,6,"Evaṃ kho, māṇava, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti. "
355947,93,868,2,29,1,126,18,"453.‘‘ Ayaṃ kho so, māṇava, ariyo sīlakkhandho yassa so bhagavā vaṇṇavādī ahosi, yattha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesi. "
355948,93,868,30,36,1,33,4,Atthi cevettha uttarikaraṇīyan’’ ti.
355949,93,869,2,13,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Acchariyaṃ, bho ānanda, abbhutaṃ, bho ānanda! "
355950,93,869,14,26,1,62,9,"So cāyaṃ, bho ānanda, ariyo sīlakkhandho paripuṇṇo, no aparipuṇṇo. "
355951,93,869,27,45,1,107,13,"Evaṃ paripuṇṇaṃ cāhaṃ, bho, ānanda, ariyaṃ sīlakkhandhaṃ ito bahiddhā aññesu samaṇabrāhmaṇesu na samanupassāmi. "
355952,93,869,46,65,1,135,16,"Evaṃ paripuṇṇañca, bho ānanda, ariyaṃ sīlakkhandhaṃ ito bahiddhā aññe samaṇabrāhmaṇā attani samanupasseyyuṃ, te tāvatakeneva attamanā assu–"
355953,93,869,66,81,1,86,10,"‘ alamettāvatā, katamettāvatā, anuppatto no sāmaññattho, natthi no kiñci uttarikaraṇīyan’ ti. "
355954,93,869,82,88,1,34,6,Atha ca pana bhavaṃ ānando evamāha–
355955,93,869,89,114,1,33,4,‘ atthi cevettha uttarikaraṇīyan’’’ ti[ imassa anantaraṃ sī. pī. potthakesu‘‘ paṭhamabhāṇavāraṃ’’ ti pāṭho dissati]. 
355956,93,870,2,2,1,15,1,Samādhikkhandho 
355957,93,871,2,36,1,145,21,"454.‘‘ Katamo pana so, bho ānanda, ariyo samādhikkhandho, yassa so bhavaṃ gotamo vaṇṇavādī ahosi, yattha ca imaṃ janataṃ samādapesi nivesesi patiṭṭhāpesī’’ ti?"
355958,93,872,2,12,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, māṇava, bhikkhu indriyesu guttadvāro hoti? "
355959,93,872,13,25,1,79,10,"Idha, māṇava, bhikkhu cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā na nimittaggāhī hoti nānubyañjanaggāhī; "
355960,93,872,26,45,1,190,17,"yatvādhikaraṇamenaṃ cakkhundriyaṃ asaṃvutaṃ viharantaṃ abhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā dhammā anvāssaveyyuṃ tassa saṃvarāya paṭipajjati, rakkhati cakkhundriyaṃ, cakkhundriye saṃvaraṃ āpajjati. "
355961,93,872,46,72,1,159,20,Sotena saddaṃ sutvā… pe… ghānena gandhaṃ ghāyitvā… jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā… kāyena phoṭṭhabbaṃ phusitvā… manasā dhammaṃ viññāya na nimittaggāhī hoti nānubyañjanaggāhī; 
355962,93,872,73,92,1,184,17,"yatvādhikaraṇamenaṃ manindriyaṃ asaṃvutaṃ viharantaṃ abhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā dhammā anvāssaveyyuṃ tassa saṃvarāya paṭipajjati, rakkhati manindriyaṃ, manindriye saṃvaraṃ āpajjati. "
355963,93,872,93,101,1,84,8,So iminā ariyena indriyasaṃvarena samannāgato ajjhattaṃ abyāsekasukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. 
355964,93,872,102,111,1,49,7,"Evaṃ kho, māṇava, bhikkhu indriyesu guttadvāro hoti. "
355965,93,873,2,16,1,57,6,"455.‘‘ Kathañca, māṇava, bhikkhu satisampajaññena samannāgato hoti? "
355966,93,873,17,62,1,335,36,"Idha, māṇava, bhikkhu abhikkante paṭikkante sampajānakārī hoti, ālokite vilokite sampajānakārī hoti, samiñjite pasārite sampajānakārī hoti, saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇe sampajānakārī hoti, asite pīte khāyite sāyite sampajānakārī hoti, uccārapassāvakamme sampajānakārī hoti, gate ṭhite nisinne sutte jāgarite bhāsite tuṇhībhāve sampajānakārī hoti. "
355967,93,873,63,72,1,57,7,"Evaṃ kho, māṇava, bhikkhu satisampajaññena samannāgato hoti. "
355968,93,874,2,15,1,38,5,"456.‘‘ Kathañca, māṇava, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti? "
355969,93,874,16,27,1,91,9,"Idha, māṇava, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti kāyaparihārikena cīvarena kucchiparihārikena piṇḍapātena. "
355970,93,874,28,35,1,45,6,"So yena yeneva pakkamati, samādāyeva pakkamati. "
355971,93,874,36,49,1,68,9,"Seyyathāpi, māṇava, pakkhī sakuṇo yena yeneva ḍeti, sapattabhārova ḍeti ; "
355972,93,874,50,62,1,98,10,"evameva kho, māṇava, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti kāyaparihārikena cīvarena kucchiparihārikena piṇḍapātena. "
355973,93,874,63,70,1,45,6,"So yena yeneva pakkamati, samādāyeva pakkamati. "
355974,93,874,71,79,1,38,6,"Evaṃ kho, māṇava, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti. "
355975,93,875,2,45,1,298,33,"457.‘‘ So iminā ca ariyena sīlakkhandhena samannāgato, iminā ca ariyena indriyasaṃvarena samannāgato, iminā ca ariyena satisampajaññena samannāgato, imāya ca ariyāya santuṭṭhiyā samannāgato vivittaṃ senāsanaṃ bhajati araññaṃ rukkhamūlaṃ pabbataṃ kandaraṃ giriguhaṃ susānaṃ vanapatthaṃ abbhokāsaṃ palālapuñjaṃ. "
355976,93,875,46,60,1,117,12,"So pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātappaṭikkanto nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā, ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya, parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. "
355977,93,876,2,18,1,86,10,458.‘‘ So abhijjhaṃ loke pahāya vigatābhijjhena cetasā viharati abhijjhāya cittaṃ parisodheti. 
355978,93,876,19,27,1,104,8,Byāpādapadosaṃ pahāya abyāpannacitto viharati sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī byāpādapadosā cittaṃ parisodheti. 
355979,93,876,28,39,1,103,10,"Thinamiddhaṃ pahāya vigatathinamiddho viharati ālokasaññī sato sampajāno, thinamiddhā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
355980,93,876,40,49,1,104,9,Uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahāya anuddhato viharati ajjhattaṃ vūpasantacitto uddhaccakukkuccā cittaṃ parisodheti. 
355981,93,876,50,61,1,106,10,"Vicikicchaṃ pahāya tiṇṇavicikiccho viharati akathaṃkathī kusalesu dhammesu, vicikicchāya cittaṃ parisodheti. "
355982,93,877,2,17,1,54,7,"459.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso iṇaṃ ādāya kammante payojeyya. "
355983,93,877,18,22,1,30,4,Tassa te kammantā samijjheyyuṃ. 
355984,93,877,23,39,1,97,14,"So yāni ca porāṇāni iṇamūlāni tāni ca byantiṃ kareyya, siyā cassa uttariṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ dārabharaṇāya. "
355985,93,877,40,42,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
355986,93,877,43,52,1,44,7,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe iṇaṃ ādāya kammante payojesiṃ . 
355987,93,877,53,58,1,32,5,Tassa me te kammantā samijjhiṃsu. 
355988,93,877,59,77,1,103,16,"Sohaṃ yāni ca porāṇāni iṇamūlāni tāni ca byantiṃ akāsiṃ, atthi ca me uttariṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ dārabharaṇāyā’ ti. "
355989,93,877,78,85,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
355990,93,878,2,17,1,59,7,"460.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso ābādhiko assa dukkhito bāḷhagilāno; "
355991,93,878,18,25,1,48,6,"bhattañcassa nacchādeyya, na cassa kāye balamattā. "
355992,93,878,26,40,1,89,12,"So aparena samayena tamhā ābādhā mucceyya, bhattañcassa chādeyya, siyā cassa kāye balamattā. "
355993,93,878,41,43,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
355994,93,878,44,63,1,103,16,"‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe ābādhiko ahosiṃ dukkhito bāḷhagilāno, bhattañca me nacchādesi, na ca me āsi kāye balamattā. "
355995,93,878,64,80,1,83,14,"Somhi etarahi tamhā ābādhā mutto bhattañca me chādeti, atthi ca me kāye balamattā’ ti. "
355996,93,878,81,88,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
355997,93,879,2,16,1,49,6,"461.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso bandhanāgāre baddho assa. "
355998,93,879,17,31,1,95,13,"So aparena samayena tamhā bandhanāgārā mucceyya sotthinā abbhayena, na cassa kiñci bhogānaṃ vayo. "
355999,93,879,32,34,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
356000,93,879,35,42,1,41,6,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe bandhanāgāre baddho ahosiṃ. 
356001,93,879,43,60,1,93,14,"Somhi etarahi tamhā bandhanāgārā mutto sotthinā abbhayena, natthi ca me kiñci bhogānaṃ vayo’ ti. "
356002,93,879,61,68,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
356003,93,880,2,19,1,73,9,"462.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso dāso assa anattādhīno parādhīno na yenakāmaṃgamo. "
356004,93,880,20,32,1,86,10,"So aparena samayena tamhā dāsabyā mucceyya, attādhīno aparādhīno bhujisso yenakāmaṃgamo. "
356005,93,880,33,35,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa–
356006,93,880,36,46,1,65,9,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe dāso ahosiṃ anattādhīno parādhīno na yenakāmaṃgamo. 
356007,93,880,47,58,1,80,10,Somhi etarahi tamhā dāsabyā mutto attādhīno aparādhīno bhujisso yenakāmaṃgamo’ ti. 
356008,93,880,59,66,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
356009,93,881,2,19,1,99,9,"463.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, puriso sadhano sabhogo kantāraddhānamaggaṃ paṭipajjeyya dubbhikkhaṃ sappaṭibhayaṃ. "
356010,93,881,20,32,1,95,11,"So aparena samayena taṃ kantāraṃ nitthareyya, sotthinā gāmantaṃ anupāpuṇeyya khemaṃ appaṭibhayaṃ. "
356011,93,881,33,36,1,14,2,Tassa evamassa –
356012,93,881,37,47,1,87,9,‘ ahaṃ kho pubbe sadhano sabhogo kantāraddhānamaggaṃ paṭipajjiṃ dubbhikkhaṃ sappaṭibhayaṃ. 
356013,93,881,48,60,1,83,10,"Somhi etarahi kantāraṃ nitthiṇṇo, sotthinā gāmantaṃ anuppatto khemaṃ appaṭibhayan’ ti. "
356014,93,881,61,68,1,57,6,"So tatonidānaṃ labhetha pāmojjaṃ, adhigaccheyya somanassaṃ. "
356015,93,882,2,32,1,164,21,"464.‘‘ Evameva kho, māṇava, bhikkhu yathā iṇaṃ yathā rogaṃ yathā bandhanāgāraṃ yathā dāsabyaṃ yathā kantāraddhānamaggaṃ, evaṃ ime pañca nīvaraṇe appahīne attani samanupassati. "
356016,93,883,2,22,1,104,12,"465.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, yathā āṇaṇyaṃ yathā ārogyaṃ yathā bandhanāmokkhaṃ yathā bhujissaṃ yathā khemantabhūmiṃ. "
356017,93,883,23,31,1,62,8,Evameva bhikkhu ime pañca nīvaraṇe pahīne attani samanupassati. 
356018,93,884,2,32,1,174,20,"466.‘‘ Tassime pañca nīvaraṇe pahīne attani samanupassato pāmojjaṃ jāyati, pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vedeti, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
356019,93,885,2,22,1,125,14,467.‘‘ So vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
356020,93,885,23,43,1,154,17,"So imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
356021,93,886,2,20,1,133,15,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, māṇava, dakkho nhāpako vā nhāpakantevāsī vā kaṃsathāle nhānīyacuṇṇāni ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ paripphosakaṃ sandeyya. "
356022,93,886,21,32,1,87,10,"Sāyaṃ nhānīyapiṇḍi snehānugatā snehaparetā santarabāhirā phuṭā snehena, na ca paggharaṇī. "
356023,93,886,33,56,1,178,20,"Evameva kho, māṇava, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati, nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti. "
356024,93,886,57,75,1,143,16,"Yampi, māṇava, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
