356215,93,922,14,22,1,58,6,"Idha, kevaṭṭa, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti. "
356216,93,922,23,32,1,49,8,"Ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi hutvā eko hoti; "
356217,93,922,33,42,1,93,9,āvibhāvaṃ tirobhāvaṃ tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno gacchati seyyathāpi ākāse; 
356218,93,922,43,48,1,51,5,pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ karoti seyyathāpi udake; 
