356220,93,922,55,61,1,50,6,ākāsepi pallaṅkena kamati seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo; 
356221,93,922,62,71,1,82,9,imepi candimasūriye evaṃ mahiddhike evaṃ mahānubhāve pāṇinā parāmasati parimajjati; 
356222,93,922,72,77,1,38,5,yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti.
