356346,93,952,33,39,1,53,6,Te atīradakkhiniyā nāvāya tīradassiṃ sakuṇaṃ muñcanti. 
356347,93,952,40,63,1,144,18,"So gacchateva puratthimaṃ disaṃ, gacchati dakkhiṇaṃ disaṃ, gacchati pacchimaṃ disaṃ, gacchati uttaraṃ disaṃ, gacchati uddhaṃ disaṃ, gacchati anudisaṃ. "
