356359,93,959,2,11,1,41,8,"Ettha āpo ca pathavī, tejo vāyo na gādhati. "
356360,93,960,2,9,1,47,6,"Ettha dīghañca rassañca, aṇuṃ thūlaṃ subhāsubhaṃ; "
356361,93,961,2,8,1,40,5,"Ettha nāmañca rūpañca, asesaṃ uparujjhati; "
356362,93,962,2,9,1,44,5,"Viññāṇassa nirodhena, etthetaṃ uparujjhatī’ ti. "
356363,93,963,2,9,1,17,2,500. Idamavoca bhagavā. 
356364,93,963,10,16,1,61,6,Attamano kevaṭṭo gahapatiputto bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. 
356365,93,964,2,5,1,34,3,Kevaṭṭasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ ekādasamaṃ. 
356366,93,965,2,5,1,13,1,12. Lohiccasuttaṃ 
356367,93,966,2,2,1,21,1,Lohiccabrāhmaṇavatthu 
356368,93,967,2,28,1,145,17,501. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi yena sālavatikā tadavasari. 
356369,93,967,29,48,1,171,18,"Tena kho pana samayena lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ, brahmadeyyaṃ. "
356370,93,968,2,17,1,88,11,502. Tena kho pana samayena lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ hoti–
356371,93,968,18,40,1,132,18,"‘‘ idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati. "
356372,93,968,41,63,1,150,18,"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya, evaṃsampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi, kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’’ ti. "
356373,93,969,2,10,1,27,4,503. Assosi kho lohicco brāhmaṇo–
356374,93,969,11,32,1,160,17,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sālavatikaṃ anuppatto. "
356375,93,969,33,42,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
356376,93,969,43,59,1,139,14,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’. 
356377,93,969,60,74,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
356378,93,969,75,88,1,135,12,So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. 
356379,93,969,89,99,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
356380,93,970,2,23,1,51,7,504. Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo rosikaṃ[ bhesikaṃ( sī. pī.)] nhāpitaṃ āmantesi–
356381,93,970,24,37,1,54,8,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, samma rosike, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkama ; "
356382,93,970,38,67,1,214,24,"upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ puccha– lohicco, bho gotama, brāhmaṇo bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchatī’’ ti. "
356383,93,970,68,70,1,13,2,Evañca vadehi–
356384,93,970,71,86,1,97,11,‘‘ adhivāsetu kira bhavaṃ gotamo lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’’ ti. 
356385,93,971,2,33,1,91,12,"505.‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti[ evaṃ bhanteti( sī. pī.)] kho rosikā nhāpito lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
356386,93,971,34,39,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
356387,93,971,40,47,1,58,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
356388,93,971,48,62,1,97,10,"‘‘ lohicco, bhante, brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati; "
356389,93,971,63,81,1,112,13,"evañca vadeti– adhivāsetu kira, bhante, bhagavā lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’’ ti. "
356390,93,971,82,85,1,31,3,Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. 
356391,93,972,2,22,1,143,16,506. Atha kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā yena lohicco brāhmaṇo tenupasaṅkami; 
356392,93,972,23,27,1,42,4,upasaṅkamitvā lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca–
356393,93,972,28,48,1,49,7,‘‘ avocumhā kho mayaṃ bhoto[ mayaṃ bhante tava( sī. pī.)] vacanena taṃ bhagavantaṃ–
356394,93,972,49,64,1,97,10,"‘ lohicco, bhante, brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati; "
356395,93,972,65,82,1,112,13,"evañca vadeti– adhivāsetu kira, bhante, bhagavā lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā’ ti. "
356396,93,972,83,90,1,36,5,Adhivutthañca pana tena bhagavatā’’ ti. 
356397,93,973,2,22,1,132,16,507. Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo tassā rattiyā accayena sake nivesane paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā rosikaṃ nhāpitaṃ āmantesi–
356398,93,973,23,35,1,54,8,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, samma rosike, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkama; "
356399,93,973,36,52,1,84,11,"upasaṅkamitvā samaṇassa gotamassa kālaṃ ārocehi– kālo bho, gotama, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan’’ ti."
356400,93,973,53,70,1,91,12,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho rosikā nhāpito lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
356401,93,973,71,77,1,55,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi . 
356402,93,973,78,86,1,58,8,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavato kālaṃ ārocesi–
356403,93,973,87,98,1,32,5,"‘‘ kālo, bhante, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan’’ ti. "
356404,93,974,2,18,1,114,11,508. Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena yena sālavatikā tenupasaṅkami. 
356405,93,974,19,30,1,82,11,Tena kho pana samayena rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti. 
356406,93,974,31,37,1,45,6,Atha kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
356407,93,974,38,49,1,67,7,"‘‘ lohiccassa, bhante, brāhmaṇassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ–"
356408,93,974,50,71,1,132,18,"‘ idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya– kiñhi paro parassa karissati. "
356409,93,974,72,95,1,151,19,"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya, evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi– kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’ ti. "
356410,93,974,96,110,1,76,10,"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etasmā pāpakā diṭṭhigatā vivecetū’’ ti."
356411,93,974,111,125,1,50,9,"‘‘ Appeva nāma siyā rosike, appeva nāma siyā rosike’’ ti. "
356412,93,975,2,10,1,68,8,Atha kho bhagavā yena lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; 
356413,93,975,11,16,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi . 
356414,93,975,17,29,1,121,12,Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi. 
356415,93,976,2,2,1,21,1,Lohiccabrāhmaṇānuyogo 
356416,93,977,2,19,1,111,13,509. Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
356417,93,977,20,27,1,59,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
356418,93,977,28,40,1,60,8,"‘‘ saccaṃ kira te, lohicca, evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ–"
356419,93,977,41,62,1,132,18,"‘ idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya– kiñhi paro parassa karissati. "
356420,93,977,63,87,1,151,19,"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya, evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi, kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’’’ ti?"
356421,93,977,88,96,1,15,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho gotama’’."
356422,93,977,97,110,1,60,9,‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññasi lohicca nanu tvaṃ sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasasī’’ ti?
356423,93,977,111,119,1,15,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho gotama’’."
356424,93,977,120,130,1,30,6,"‘‘ Yo nu kho, lohicca, evaṃ vadeyya–"
356425,93,977,131,136,1,40,4,‘ lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati. 
356426,93,977,137,152,1,96,12,"Yā sālavatikāya samudayasañjāti lohiccova taṃ brāhmaṇo ekako paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ ti. "
356427,93,977,153,171,1,66,13,"Evaṃ vādī so ye taṃ upajīvanti, tesaṃ antarāyakaro vā hoti, no vā’’ ti?"
356428,93,978,2,10,1,23,4,"‘ ‘ Antarāyakaro, bho gotama’’."
356429,93,978,11,24,1,64,9,‘‘ Antarāyakaro samāno hitānukampī vā tesaṃ hoti ahitānukampī vā’’ ti?
356430,93,978,25,33,1,23,3,"‘‘ Ahitānukampī, bho gotama’’."
356431,93,978,34,48,1,74,10,‘‘ Ahitānukampissa mettaṃ vā tesu cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sapattakaṃ vā’’ ti?
356432,93,978,49,57,1,21,3,"‘‘ Sapattakaṃ, bho gotama’’."
356433,93,978,58,72,1,68,9,‘‘ Sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi vā hoti sammādiṭṭhi vā’’ ti?
356434,93,978,73,81,1,23,3,"‘‘ Micchādiṭṭhi, bho gotama’’."
356435,93,978,82,102,1,101,13,"‘‘ Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi– nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā’’. "
356436,93,979,2,23,1,76,11,"510.‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, lohicca, nanu rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasatī’’ ti?"
356437,93,979,24,32,1,15,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho gotama’’."
356438,93,979,33,43,1,30,6,"‘‘ Yo nu kho, lohicca, evaṃ vadeyya–"
356439,93,979,44,50,1,44,5,‘ rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasati; 
356440,93,979,51,67,1,98,13,"yā kāsikosale samudayasañjāti, rājāva taṃ pasenadi kosalo ekako paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ ti. "
356441,93,979,68,91,1,107,19,"Evaṃ vādī so ye rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ upajīvanti tumhe ceva aññe ca, tesaṃ antarāyakaro vā hoti, no vā’’ ti?"
356442,93,980,2,10,1,23,4,"‘ ‘ Antarāyakaro, bho gotama’’."
356443,93,980,11,24,1,64,9,‘‘ Antarāyakaro samāno hitānukampī vā tesaṃ hoti ahitānukampī vā’’ ti?
356444,93,980,25,33,1,23,3,"‘‘ Ahitānukampī, bho gotama’’."
356445,93,980,34,48,1,74,10,‘‘ Ahitānukampissa mettaṃ vā tesu cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sapattakaṃ vā’’ ti?
356446,93,980,49,57,1,21,3,"‘‘ Sapattakaṃ, bho gotama’’."
356447,93,980,58,71,1,68,9,‘‘ Sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi vā hoti sammādiṭṭhi vā’’ ti?
356448,93,980,72,80,1,23,3,"‘‘ Micchādiṭṭhi, bho gotama’’."
356449,93,980,81,102,1,101,13,"‘‘ Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi– nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā’’. "
356450,93,981,2,17,1,32,6,"511.‘‘ Iti kira, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya–"
356451,93,981,18,24,1,40,4,‘‘ lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati; 
356452,93,981,25,41,1,96,12,"yā sālavatikāya samudayasañjāti, lohiccova taṃ brāhmaṇo ekako paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’’ ti. "
356453,93,981,42,51,1,53,8,"Evaṃvādī so ye taṃ upajīvanti, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti. "
356454,93,981,52,68,1,139,14,"Antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti. "
356455,93,981,69,77,1,35,6,"Evameva kho, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya–"
356456,93,981,78,101,1,132,18,"‘‘ idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati. "
356457,93,981,102,118,1,89,12,Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya… pe… karissatī’’ ti. 
356458,93,981,119,174,1,457,45,"Evaṃvādī so ye te kulaputtā tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ āgamma evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchanti, sotāpattiphalampi sacchikaronti, sakadāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, anāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, arahattampi sacchikaronti, ye cime dibbā gabbhā paripācenti dibbānaṃ bhavānaṃ abhinibbattiyā, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti, antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti , ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti. "
356459,93,981,175,191,1,101,13,"Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi– nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā. "
356460,93,982,2,16,1,32,6,"512.‘‘ Iti kira, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya–"
356461,93,982,17,24,1,44,5,‘‘ rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasati; 
356462,93,982,25,43,1,98,13,"yā kāsikosale samudayasañjāti, rājāva taṃ pasenadi kosalo ekako paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’’ ti. "
356463,93,982,44,59,1,94,14,"Evaṃvādī so ye rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ upajīvanti tumhe ceva aññe ca, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti. "
356464,93,982,60,76,1,139,14,"Antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti. "
356465,93,982,77,85,1,35,6,"Evameva kho, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya–"
356466,93,982,86,108,1,132,18,"‘‘ idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati. "
356467,93,982,109,148,1,279,29,"Seyyathāpi nāma… pe… kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’’ ti, evaṃ vādī so ye te kulaputtā tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ āgamma evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchanti, sotāpattiphalampi sacchikaronti, sakadāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, anāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, arahattampi sacchikaronti. "
356468,93,982,149,179,1,229,25,"Ye cime dibbā gabbhā paripācenti dibbānaṃ bhavānaṃ abhinibbattiyā, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti, antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti. "
356469,93,982,180,196,1,101,13,"Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi– nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā. "
356470,93,983,2,3,1,15,2,Tayo codanārahā 
356471,93,984,2,19,1,46,7,"513.‘‘ Tayo khome, lohicca, satthāro, ye loke codanārahā; "
356472,93,984,20,33,1,73,11,"yo ca panevarūpe satthāro codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā anavajjā . "
356473,93,984,34,36,1,11,2,Katame tayo? 
356474,93,984,37,53,1,109,13,"Idha, lohicca, ekacco satthā yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti, svāssa sāmaññattho ananuppatto hoti. "
356475,93,984,54,61,1,59,7,So taṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti–
356476,93,984,62,73,1,33,7,‘‘ idaṃ vo hitāya idaṃ vo sukhāyā’’ ti. 
356477,93,984,74,93,1,106,15,"Tassa sāvakā na sussūsanti, na sotaṃ odahanti, na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti, vokkamma ca satthusāsanā vattanti. "
356478,93,984,94,97,1,21,3,So evamassa codetabbo–
356479,93,984,98,119,1,144,17,"‘‘ āyasmā kho yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito, so te sāmaññattho ananuppatto, taṃ tvaṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desesi–"
