356923,94,33,27,36,1,47,5,"‘‘ kāyanuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā; "
356924,94,33,37,46,1,38,7,kā ca pana vo antarākathā vippakatā’’ ti? 
356925,94,34,2,8,1,44,6,Evaṃ vutte te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–
356926,94,34,9,21,1,71,8,"‘‘ idha, bhante, amhākaṃ acirapakkantassa bhagavato ayaṃ antarākathā udapādi–"
