357266,94,121,2,2,1,23,1,Mahājanakāyaanupabbajjā 
357267,94,122,2,18,1,83,8,"55.‘‘ Assosi kho, bhikkhave, bandhumatiyā rājadhāniyā mahājanakāyo caturāsīti pāṇasahassāni–"
