357269,94,122,36,39,1,23,3,Sutvāna tesaṃ etadahosi–
357270,94,122,40,73,1,154,21,"‘ na hi nūna so orako dhammavinayo, na sā orakā[ orikā( sī. syā.)] pabbajjā, yattha vipassī kumāro kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito. "
357271,94,122,74,98,1,126,15,"Vipassīpi nāma kumāro kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajissati, kimaṅgaṃ[ kimaṅga( sī.)] pana mayan’ ti."
357272,94,123,2,31,1,174,19,"‘ ‘ Atha kho, so bhikkhave, mahājanakāyo[ mahājanakāyo( syā.)] caturāsīti pāṇasahassāni kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā vipassiṃ bodhisattaṃ agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajitaṃ anupabbajiṃsu. "
357273,94,123,32,44,1,102,10,"Tāya sudaṃ, bhikkhave, parisāya parivuto vipassī bodhisatto gāmanigamajanapadarājadhānīsu cārikaṃ carati. "
357274,94,124,2,21,1,102,11,"56.‘‘ Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi–"
