357674,94,231,2,31,1,85,12,95. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kurūsu viharati kammāsadhammaṃ nāma[ kammāsadammaṃ nāma( syā.)] kurūnaṃ nigamo. 
357675,94,231,32,45,1,104,12,"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
357676,94,231,46,53,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
357677,94,231,54,63,1,33,4,"‘‘ acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante! "
357678,94,231,64,84,1,110,15,"Yāva gambhīro cāyaṃ, bhante, paṭiccasamuppādo gambhīrāvabhāso ca, atha ca pana me uttānakuttānako viya khāyatī’’ ti."
357679,94,231,85,100,1,43,8,"‘‘ Mā hevaṃ, ānanda, avaca, mā hevaṃ, ānanda, avaca. "
357680,94,231,101,109,1,57,6,"Gambhīro cāyaṃ, ānanda, paṭiccasamuppādo gambhīrāvabhāso ca. "
357681,94,231,110,142,1,158,15,"Etassa, ānanda, dhammassa ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamayaṃ pajā tantākulakajātā kulagaṇṭhikajātā[ gulāguṇṭhikajātā( sī. pī.), guṇagaṇṭhikajātā( syā.)] muñjapabbajabhūtā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ saṃsāraṃ nātivattati. "
357682,94,232,2,22,1,78,10,"96.‘‘‘ Atthi idappaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ ti iti puṭṭhena satā, ānanda, atthītissa vacanīyaṃ."
357683,94,232,23,39,1,85,11,"‘ Kiṃpaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ ti iti ce vadeyya,‘ jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ ti iccassa vacanīyaṃ."
357684,94,233,2,19,1,71,11,"‘ ‘‘ Atthi idappaccayā jātī’ ti iti puṭṭhena satā, ānanda, atthītissa vacanīyaṃ."
