357729,94,249,2,29,1,130,16,"105.‘‘‘ Macchariyaṃ paṭicca ārakkho’ ti iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ, tadānanda, imināpetaṃ pariyāyena veditabbaṃ, yathā macchariyaṃ paṭicca ārakkho. "
