357836,94,273,2,2,1,17,1,Attasamanupassanā 
357837,94,274,2,17,1,57,6,"121.‘‘ Kittāvatā ca, ānanda, attānaṃ samanupassamāno samanupassati? "
357838,94,274,18,27,1,58,7,"Vedanaṃ vā hi, ānanda, attānaṃ samanupassamāno samanupassati–"
357839,94,274,28,34,1,17,4,‘ vedanā me attā’ ti.
357840,94,274,35,57,1,108,17,"‘ Na heva kho me vedanā attā, appaṭisaṃvedano me attā’ ti iti vā hi, ānanda, attānaṃ samanupassamāno samanupassati."
357841,94,274,58,90,1,154,25,"‘ Na heva kho me vedanā attā, nopi appaṭisaṃvedano me attā, attā me vediyati, vedanādhammo hi me attā’ ti iti vā hi, ānanda, attānaṃ samanupassamāno samanupassati. "
357842,94,275,2,13,1,24,4,"122.‘‘ Tatrānanda, yo so evamāha–"
357843,94,275,14,24,1,38,7,"‘ vedanā me attā’ ti, so evamassa vacanīyo–"
357844,94,275,25,40,1,75,11,"‘ tisso kho imā, āvuso, vedanā– sukhā vedanā dukkhā vedanā adukkhamasukhā vedanā. "
