358166,94,363,28,59,1,76,8,"Tena samayena sambahulā devatāyo sahasseva[ sahassasseva( sī. pī. ka.), sahassaseva( ṭīkāyaṃ pāṭhantaraṃ), sahassasahasseva( udānaṭṭhakathā)] pāṭaligāme vatthūni pariggaṇhanti. "
