359592,94,678,43,60,1,153,15,"Bhūtapubbaṃ, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tameva maṇiratanaṃ vīmaṃsamāno caturaṅginiṃ senaṃ sannayhitvā maṇiṃ dhajaggaṃ āropetvā rattandhakāratimisāya pāyāsi. "
359593,94,678,61,75,1,87,12,"Ye kho panānanda, samantā gāmā ahesuṃ, te tenobhāsena kammante payojesuṃ divāti maññamānā. "
359594,94,678,76,84,1,61,6,"Rañño, ānanda, mahāsudassanassa evarūpaṃ maṇiratanaṃ pāturahosi. "
359595,94,679,2,2,1,12,1,Itthiratanaṃ 
359596,94,680,2,40,1,236,23,"249.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa itthiratanaṃ pāturahosi abhirūpā dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā nātidīghā nātirassā nātikisā nātithūlā nātikāḷikā nāccodātā atikkantā mānusivaṇṇaṃ[ mānussivaṇṇaṃ( syā.)] appattā dibbavaṇṇaṃ. "
359597,94,680,41,58,1,108,13,"Tassa kho panānanda, itthiratanassa evarūpo kāyasamphasso hoti, seyyathāpi nāma tūlapicuno vā kappāsapicuno vā. "
359598,94,680,59,71,1,72,10,"Tassa kho panānanda, itthiratanassa sīte uṇhāni gattāni honti, uṇhe sītāni. "
359599,94,680,72,83,1,83,9,"Tassa kho panānanda, itthiratanassa kāyato candanagandho vāyati, mukhato uppalagandho. "
359600,94,680,84,98,1,131,12,"Taṃ kho panānanda, itthiratanaṃ rañño mahāsudassanassa pubbuṭṭhāyinī ahosi pacchānipātinī kiṅkārapaṭissāvinī manāpacārinī piyavādinī. "
359601,94,680,99,130,1,90,12,"Taṃ kho panānanda, itthiratanaṃ rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ manasāpi no aticari[ aticarī( ka.), aticārī( sī. syā. pī.)], kuto pana kāyena. "
359602,94,680,131,139,1,62,6,"Rañño, ānanda, mahāsudassanassa evarūpaṃ itthiratanaṃ pāturahosi. "
359603,94,681,2,2,1,15,1,Gahapatiratanaṃ 
359604,94,682,2,17,1,69,7,"250.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa gahapatiratanaṃ pāturahosi. "
359605,94,682,18,27,1,88,9,Tassa kammavipākajaṃ dibbacakkhu pāturahosi yena nidhiṃ passati sassāmikampi assāmikampi. 
359606,94,682,28,33,1,47,5,So rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāha–
359607,94,682,34,49,1,69,10,"‘ appossukko tvaṃ, deva, hohi, ahaṃ te dhanena dhanakaraṇīyaṃ karissāmī’ ti. "
359608,94,682,50,69,1,153,16,"Bhūtapubbaṃ, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tameva gahapatiratanaṃ vīmaṃsamāno nāvaṃ abhiruhitvā majjhe gaṅgāya nadiyā sotaṃ ogāhitvā gahapatiratanaṃ etadavoca–"
359609,94,682,70,79,1,37,5,"‘ attho me, gahapati, hiraññasuvaṇṇenā’ ti."
359610,94,682,80,92,1,41,8,"‘ Tena hi, mahārāja, ekaṃ tīraṃ nāvā upetū’ ti."
359611,94,682,93,103,1,44,6,"‘ Idheva me, gahapati, attho hiraññasuvaṇṇenā’ ti. "
359612,94,682,104,123,1,143,16,"Atha kho taṃ, ānanda, gahapatiratanaṃ ubhohi hatthehi udakaṃ omasitvā pūraṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇassa kumbhiṃ uddharitvā rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ etadavoca –"
359613,94,682,124,135,1,72,7,"‘ alamettāvatā mahārāja, katamettāvatā mahārāja, pūjitamettāvatā mahārājā’ ti? "
359614,94,682,136,139,1,26,3,Rājā mahāsudassano evamāha–
359615,94,682,140,151,1,72,7,"‘ alamettāvatā gahapati, katamettāvatā gahapati, pūjitamettāvatā gahapatī’ ti. "
359616,94,682,152,161,1,65,6,"Rañño , ānanda, mahāsudassanassa evarūpaṃ gahapatiratanaṃ pāturahosi. "
