359625,94,687,18,21,1,23,3,Katamāhi catūhi iddhīhi? 
359626,94,687,22,36,1,126,13,"Idhānanda, rājā mahāsudassano abhirūpo ahosi dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato ativiya aññehi manussehi. "
