359631,94,689,24,34,1,66,8,"Rājā, ānanda, mahāsudassano imāya tatiyāya iddhiyā samannāgato ahosi."
359632,94,690,2,16,1,78,10,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ , ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano brāhmaṇagahapatikānaṃ piyo ahosi manāpo. "
359633,94,690,17,38,1,126,16,"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, pitā puttānaṃ piyo hoti manāpo, evameva kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano brāhmaṇagahapatikānaṃ piyo ahosi manāpo. "
359634,94,690,39,48,1,69,7,"Raññopi, ānanda, mahāsudassanassa brāhmaṇagahapatikā piyā ahesuṃ manāpā. "
359635,94,690,49,70,1,128,16,"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, pitu puttā piyā honti manāpā, evameva kho, ānanda, raññopi mahāsudassanassa brāhmaṇagahapatikā piyā ahesuṃ manāpā."
359636,94,691,2,14,1,79,9,"‘ ‘ Bhūtapubbaṃ, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano caturaṅginiyā senāya uyyānabhūmiṃ niyyāsi. "
359637,94,691,15,25,1,82,8,"Atha kho, ānanda, brāhmaṇagahapatikā rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu–"
359638,94,691,26,41,1,59,9,"‘ ataramāno, deva, yāhi, yathā taṃ mayaṃ cirataraṃ passeyyāmā’ ti. "
