359643,94,692,2,2,1,22,1,Dhammapāsādapokkharaṇī 
359644,94,693,2,16,1,48,6,"253.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359645,94,693,17,27,1,75,8,‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ imāsu tālantarikāsu dhanusate dhanusate pokkharaṇiyo māpeyyan’ ti.
359646,94,694,2,16,1,88,11,"‘ ‘ Māpesi kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tāsu tālantarikāsu dhanusate dhanusate pokkharaṇiyo. "
359647,94,694,17,40,1,141,18,"Tā kho panānanda, pokkharaṇiyo catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ iṭṭhakāhi citā ahesuṃ– ekā iṭṭhakā sovaṇṇamayā, ekā rūpiyamayā, ekā veḷuriyamayā, ekā phalikamayā."
359648,94,695,2,25,1,161,20,"‘ ‘ Tāsu kho panānanda, pokkharaṇīsu cattāri cattāri sopānāni ahesuṃ catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ, ekaṃ sopānaṃ sovaṇṇamayaṃ ekaṃ rūpiyamayaṃ ekaṃ veḷuriyamayaṃ ekaṃ phalikamayaṃ. "
359649,94,695,26,38,1,82,9,"Sovaṇṇamayassa sopānassa sovaṇṇamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, rūpiyamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359650,94,695,39,49,1,81,9,"Rūpiyamayassa sopānassa rūpiyamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, sovaṇṇamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359651,94,695,50,60,1,85,9,"Veḷuriyamayassa sopānassa veḷuriyamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, phalikamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359652,94,695,61,71,1,84,9,"Phalikamayassa sopānassa phalikamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, veḷuriyamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359653,94,695,72,87,1,101,13,"Tā kho panānanda, pokkharaṇiyo dvīhi vedikāhi parikkhittā ahesuṃ ekā vedikā sovaṇṇamayā, ekā rūpiyamayā. "
359654,94,695,88,98,1,80,9,"Sovaṇṇamayāya vedikāya sovaṇṇamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, rūpiyamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359655,94,695,99,109,1,79,9,"Rūpiyamayāya vedikāya rūpiyamayā thambhā ahesuṃ, sovaṇṇamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. "
359656,94,695,110,119,1,48,6,"Atha kho, ānanda , rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359657,94,695,120,136,1,126,14,‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ imāsu pokkharaṇīsu evarūpaṃ mālaṃ ropāpeyyaṃ uppalaṃ padumaṃ kumudaṃ puṇḍarīkaṃ sabbotukaṃ sabbajanassa anāvaṭan’ ti. 
359658,94,695,137,156,1,139,16,"Ropāpesi kho , ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tāsu pokkharaṇīsu evarūpaṃ mālaṃ uppalaṃ padumaṃ kumudaṃ puṇḍarīkaṃ sabbotukaṃ sabbajanassa anāvaṭaṃ. "
359659,94,696,2,16,1,48,6,"254.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359660,94,696,17,32,1,96,12,"‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ imāsaṃ pokkharaṇīnaṃ tīre nhāpake purise ṭhapeyyaṃ, ye āgatāgataṃ janaṃ nhāpessantī’ ti. "
359661,94,696,33,50,1,106,14,"Ṭhapesi kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tāsaṃ pokkharaṇīnaṃ tīre nhāpake purise, ye āgatāgataṃ janaṃ nhāpesuṃ."
359662,94,697,2,12,1,48,7,"‘ ‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359663,94,697,13,65,1,249,24,"‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ imāsaṃ pokkharaṇīnaṃ tīre evarūpaṃ dānaṃ paṭṭhapeyyaṃ– annaṃ annaṭṭhikassa[ annatthitassa( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.), evaṃ sabbattha pakabhirūpeneva dissati], pānaṃ pānaṭṭhikassa, vatthaṃ vatthaṭṭhikassa, yānaṃ yānaṭṭhikassa, sayanaṃ sayanaṭṭhikassa, itthiṃ itthiṭṭhikassa, hiraññaṃ hiraññaṭṭhikassa, suvaṇṇaṃ suvaṇṇaṭṭhikassā’ ti. "
359664,94,697,66,103,1,262,26,"Paṭṭhapesi kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tāsaṃ pokkharaṇīnaṃ tīre evarūpaṃ dānaṃ– annaṃ annaṭṭhikassa, pānaṃ pānaṭṭhikassa, vatthaṃ vatthaṭṭhikassa, yānaṃ yānaṭṭhikassa, sayanaṃ sayanaṭṭhikassa, itthiṃ itthiṭṭhikassa, hiraññaṃ hiraññaṭṭhikassa, suvaṇṇaṃ suvaṇṇaṭṭhikassa. "
359665,94,698,2,21,1,107,11,"255.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, brāhmaṇagahapatikā pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ ādāya rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu–"
359666,94,698,22,39,1,79,11,"‘ idaṃ, deva, pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ devaññeva uddissa ābhataṃ, taṃ devo paṭiggaṇhatū’ ti."
359667,94,698,40,61,1,108,16,"‘ Alaṃ bho, mamapidaṃ pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ dhammikena balinā abhisaṅkhataṃ, tañca vo hotu, ito ca bhiyyo harathā’ ti. "
359668,94,698,62,70,1,58,7,Te raññā paṭikkhittā ekamantaṃ apakkamma evaṃ samacintesuṃ–
359669,94,698,71,86,1,95,13,"‘ na kho etaṃ amhākaṃ patirūpaṃ, yaṃ mayaṃ imāni sāpateyyāni punadeva sakāni gharāni paṭihareyyāma. "
359670,94,698,87,95,1,59,7,Yaṃnūna mayaṃ rañño mahāsudassanassa nivesanaṃ māpeyyāmā’ ti. 
359671,94,698,96,101,1,50,5,Te rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu–
359672,94,698,102,110,1,30,5,"‘ nivesanaṃ te deva, māpessāmā’ ti. "
359673,94,698,111,119,1,53,6,"Adhivāsesi kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tuṇhībhāvena. "
359674,94,699,2,29,1,118,12,"256.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, sakko devānamindo rañño mahāsudassanassa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya vissakammaṃ[ visukammaṃ( ka.)] devaputtaṃ āmantesi–"
359675,94,699,30,47,1,89,12,"‘ ehi tvaṃ, samma vissakamma, rañño mahāsudassanassa nivesanaṃ māpehi dhammaṃ nāma pāsādan’ ti."
359676,94,699,48,84,1,255,30,"‘ Evaṃ bhaddantavā’ ti kho, ānanda, vissakammo devaputto sakkassa devānamindassa paṭissutvā seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya, evameva devesu tāvatiṃsesu antarahito rañño mahāsudassanassa purato pāturahosi. "
359677,94,699,85,95,1,69,8,"Atha kho, ānanda, vissakammo devaputto rājānaṃ mahāsudassanaṃ etadavoca–"
359678,94,699,96,108,1,51,8,"‘ nivesanaṃ te deva, māpessāmi dhammaṃ nāma pāsādan’ ti. "
359679,94,699,109,117,1,53,6,"Adhivāsesi kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano tuṇhībhāvena."
359680,94,700,2,17,1,92,12,"‘ ‘ Māpesi kho, ānanda, vissakammo devaputto rañño mahāsudassanassa nivesanaṃ dhammaṃ nāma pāsādaṃ. "
359681,94,700,18,29,1,69,9,"Dhammo, ānanda, pāsādo puratthimena pacchimena ca yojanaṃ āyāmena ahosi. "
359682,94,700,30,35,1,46,5,Uttarena dakkhiṇena ca aḍḍhayojanaṃ vitthārena. 
359683,94,700,36,62,1,166,20,"Dhammassa, ānanda, pāsādassa tiporisaṃ uccatarena vatthu citaṃ ahosi catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ iṭṭhakāhi– ekā iṭṭhakā sovaṇṇamayā, ekā rūpiyamayā, ekā veḷuriyamayā, ekā phalikamayā."
359684,94,701,2,27,1,151,18,"‘ ‘ Dhammassa, ānanda, pāsādassa caturāsīti thambhasahassāni ahesuṃ catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ– eko thambho sovaṇṇamayo, eko rūpiyamayo, eko veḷuriyamayo, eko phalikamayo. "
359685,94,701,28,51,1,144,17,"Dhammo, ānanda, pāsādo catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ phalakehi santhato ahosi– ekaṃ phalakaṃ sovaṇṇamayaṃ, ekaṃ rūpiyamayaṃ, ekaṃ veḷuriyamayaṃ, ekaṃ phalikamayaṃ."
359686,94,702,2,27,1,151,18,"‘ ‘ Dhammassa, ānanda, pāsādassa catuvīsati sopānāni ahesuṃ catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ– ekaṃ sopānaṃ sovaṇṇamayaṃ, ekaṃ rūpiyamayaṃ, ekaṃ veḷuriyamayaṃ, ekaṃ phalikamayaṃ. "
359687,94,702,28,37,1,82,9,Sovaṇṇamayassa sopānassa sovaṇṇamayā thambhā ahesuṃ rūpiyamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. 
359688,94,702,38,47,1,81,9,Rūpiyamayassa sopānassa rūpiyamayā thambhā ahesuṃ sovaṇṇamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. 
359689,94,702,48,59,1,85,9,Veḷuriyamayassa sopānassa veḷuriyamayā thambhā ahesuṃ phalikamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca. 
359690,94,702,60,70,1,84,9,Phalikamayassa sopānassa phalikamayā thambhā ahesuṃ veḷuriyamayā sūciyo ca uṇhīsañca.
359691,94,703,2,28,1,156,18,"‘ ‘ Dhamme, ānanda, pāsāde caturāsīti kūṭāgārasahassāni ahesuṃ catunnaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ– ekaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ sovaṇṇamayaṃ, ekaṃ rūpiyamayaṃ, ekaṃ veḷuriyamayaṃ , ekaṃ phalikamayaṃ. "
359692,94,703,29,56,1,221,24,"Sovaṇṇamaye kūṭāgāre rūpiyamayo pallaṅko paññatto ahosi, rūpiyamaye kūṭāgāre sovaṇṇamayo pallaṅko paññatto ahosi, veḷuriyamaye kūṭāgāre dantamayo pallaṅko paññatto ahosi, phalikamaye kūṭāgāre sāramayo pallaṅko paññatto ahosi. "
359693,94,703,57,73,1,121,15,"Sovaṇṇamayassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre rūpiyamayo tālo ṭhito ahosi, tassa rūpiyamayo khandho sovaṇṇamayāni pattāni ca phalāni ca. "
359694,94,703,74,91,1,121,15,"Rūpiyamayassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre sovaṇṇamayo tālo ṭhito ahosi, tassa sovaṇṇamayo khandho, rūpiyamayāni pattāni ca phalāni ca. "
359695,94,703,92,109,1,125,15,"Veḷuriyamayassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre phalikamayo tālo ṭhito ahosi, tassa phalikamayo khandho, veḷuriyamayāni pattāni ca phalāni ca. "
359696,94,703,110,127,1,125,15,"Phalikamayassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre veḷuriyamayo tālo ṭhito ahosi, tassa veḷuriyamayo khandho, phalikamayāni pattāni ca phalāni ca. "
359697,94,704,2,16,1,48,6,"257.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359698,94,704,17,31,1,113,11,"‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ mahāviyūhassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre sabbasovaṇṇamayaṃ tālavanaṃ māpeyyaṃ, yattha divāvihāraṃ nisīdissāmī’ ti. "
