359738,94,713,2,17,1,48,6,"260.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359739,94,713,18,36,1,108,15,"‘ kissa nu kho me idaṃ kammassa phalaṃ kissa kammassa vipāko, yenāhaṃ etarahi evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo’ ti? "
359740,94,713,37,46,1,48,6,"Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359741,94,713,47,69,1,146,18,"‘ tiṇṇaṃ kho me idaṃ kammānaṃ phalaṃ tiṇṇaṃ kammānaṃ vipāko, yenāhaṃ etarahi evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo, seyyathidaṃ dānassa damassa saṃyamassā’ ti."
359742,94,714,2,16,1,75,10,"‘ ‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano yena mahāviyūhaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
359743,94,714,17,24,1,66,7,upasaṅkamitvā mahāviyūhassa kūṭāgārassa dvāre ṭhito udānaṃ udānesi–
359744,94,714,25,37,1,62,6,"‘ tiṭṭha, kāmavitakka, tiṭṭha, byāpādavitakka, tiṭṭha, vihiṃsāvitakka. "
359745,94,714,38,48,1,71,7,"Ettāvatā kāmavitakka, ettāvatā byāpādavitakka, ettāvatā vihiṃsāvitakkā’ ti. "
359746,94,715,2,35,1,216,24,"261.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano mahāviyūhaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ pavisitvā sovaṇṇamaye pallaṅke nisinno vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsi. "
359747,94,715,36,50,1,142,14,Vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsi. 
359748,94,715,51,69,1,109,16,"Pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca vihāsi, sato ca sampajāno sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedesi, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti–"
359749,94,715,70,80,1,65,8,‘ upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsi. 
359750,94,715,81,96,1,154,15,Sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsi. 
359751,94,716,2,30,1,177,20,"262.‘‘ Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano mahāviyūhā kūṭāgārā nikkhamitvā sovaṇṇamayaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ pavisitvā rūpiyamaye pallaṅke nisinno mettāsahagatena cetasā ekaṃ disaṃ pharitvā vihāsi. "
359752,94,716,31,37,1,43,6,Tathā dutiyaṃ tathā tatiyaṃ tathā catutthaṃ. 
359753,94,716,38,54,1,153,16,Iti uddhamadho tiriyaṃ sabbadhi sabbattatāya sabbāvantaṃ lokaṃ mettāsahagatena cetasā vipulena mahaggatena appamāṇena averena abyāpajjena pharitvā vihāsi. 
