359770,94,719,2,22,1,109,12,"264.‘‘ Tena kho panānanda, samayena rañño mahāsudassanassa caturāsīti nāgasahassāni sāyaṃ pātaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchanti. "
359771,94,719,23,31,1,48,6,"Atha kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa etadahosi–"
359772,94,719,32,56,1,194,21,"‘ imāni kho me caturāsīti nāgasahassāni sāyaṃ pātaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchanti, yaṃnūna vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena dvecattālīsaṃ dvecattālīsaṃ nāgasahassāni sakiṃ sakiṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgaccheyyun’ ti. "
359773,94,719,57,66,1,61,7,"Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano pariṇāyakaratanaṃ āmantesi–"
